(27, 8, 'tur', 'İstanbul Tours', '11bf9-istanbul-tour-back.jpg', 'af641-istanbul-tour-back.jpg', 'istanbul-Tours', 1, '', '', 1, 'İstanbul', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">İstanbul The city of the past, the present and the future. Istanbul not only joins continents, it also joins cultures and people. Close your eyes and imagine yourself in a city; the mysticism of the East and the modernity of the West, the constant time travel between past and the future, the balance of the traditional and the contemporary. Istanbul is one of the most visited and important places in the world, a central hub connecting Asia and Europe, blending the past and the future, bringing together cultures and people from all over the world. Visit Istanbul and feel the harmony of the opposites.</span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Daily', '35EUR-70EUR', 'Yes', 'Transportation', '', 'İstanbul Turları', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Стамбул Тур', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
