(36, 'Perge, Aspendos, Side Tour', 'Perge-Aspendos-Side-Tour', '4989b-aspendos.jpg', '02af8-perge-aspendos-side-tour-686x386.jpg', '2020', 26, '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:roboto,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">This is the best selling activity in Antalya.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:roboto,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">08:00&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>Meeting and move from Antalya Kaleici head office.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:roboto,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">08:45&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>Perge is 20 km east from Antalya. The tour of the ancient city is accompanied by a guide.&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:roboto,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">10:45&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>Move to the Side city.&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:roboto,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">11:15&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>Arrival to Side and one hour free time.&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:roboto,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">12:15&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>Move to Belkis village for lunch.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:roboto,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">12:45&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>The lunch break is near to Belkis river.&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:roboto,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">13:45&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>Aspendos antique theater and the Roman Aquaduct we will visit afternoon.&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:roboto,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">15:15&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>Move to the Kursunlu Waterfall.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:roboto,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">15:45&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>On the road to Isparta we will visit the Kursunlu Waterfall and the Nationa Park.&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:roboto,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">17:30&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>Arrival to Antalya.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n', '<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">PERGE:</strong>&nbsp;The ruins of the city, although not on the scale of Efhessus, Pergamon, are neverless vast. Most of today&#39; s Perge hoever, belongs to the Pax Romana-the theatre, stadium, baths and colonaded street. The stadium is one of the best preserved of the ancient world.</span></span></p>\n<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">ASPENDOS:</strong>&nbsp;Some 25 miles east of Antalya and 3 miles of the main road lies Aspendos, graced with a theatre that rivals any single adifice on the Turkish coast. Aspendos Built on the second century and seating 15.000, the structure is nearly entire except for part of the upper cornice. İt is architect was Xenon a local lad, whose secretformula for creating such perfect acoustics has not yet been discovered.</span></span></p>\n<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">SIDEE: (meaning pomegranate)</strong><br />\n	Side Is located in region of Pamphylia in Anatolia and was both a prosperous Aegean tranding centre Hellenistic and Roman times and a base for Cilicia pirates in the 1 st and 2 nd centruise BCE.</span></span></p>\n<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">KURSUNLU WATERFALLS:</strong>&nbsp;The Kursunlu Waterfalls is 18 km in distance along the Antalya -Alanya highway, which is a fascinating national park of Antalya.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Transfer service from the Hotel.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Travel with comfortable air conditioned minibus and the presence of a professional guide.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Travel incurence are included.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Drinks are excluded.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Entrance Fees &amp; Lunch are inclusive.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Head office in Antalya.</span></span></p>\n', '', '9 Hours', 0, '1', '1', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">English speaking tour guide.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	Perge, Aspendos, Side Tour,&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: roboto, sans-serif;\">erge is 20 km east from Antalya. The tour of the ancient city is accompanied by a guide.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Move to the Side city.&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Arrival to Side and one hour free time.&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Move to Belkis village for lunch.</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: roboto, sans-serif;\">The lunch break is near to Belkis river.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: roboto, sans-serif;\">Aspendos antique theater and the Roman Aquaduct we will visit afternoon.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: roboto, sans-serif;\">Move to the Kursunlu Waterfall.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: roboto, sans-serif;\">On the road to Isparta we will visit the Kursunlu Waterfall and the Nationa Park.&nbsp;</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 1, 14, ' Perge, Aspendos, Side Turu', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bu Antalya&#39;daki en &ccedil;ok satan aktivitedir</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;08:00 Antalya Kalei&ccedil;i merkez ofisine toplanma ve hareket etme</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">08:45 Perge, Antalya&#39;nın 20 km doğusundadır. Antik kentin turuna rehber eşlik ediyor.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">10:45 Side şehrine hareket/devam etme</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">11:15 Side&#39;ye varış ve bir saat boş zaman.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">12:15 &Ouml;ğle yemeği i&ccedil;in Belkıs k&ouml;y&uuml;ne gitme.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">12:45 Belkis nehrine yakın &ouml;ğle yemeği molası</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">13:45 Aspendos antik tiyatrosu ve Roma Su Kemeri &ouml;ğleden sonra ziyaret edeceğiz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">15:15 Kurşunlu Şelalesi&#39;ne gitme.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">15:45 Isparta yolunda Kurşunlu Şelalesi ve Milli Parkı ziyaret edeceğiz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">17:30 Antalya&#39;ya varış.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">PERGE: Şehrin kalıntıları, Efes ve Bergama &ouml;l&ccedil;eğinde olmasa da, yine de geniş/ b&uuml;y&uuml;k değildir. Bug&uuml;n&uuml;n Perge&rsquo;sinin &ccedil;oğunu Pax Romana&#39;ya ait - tiyatro, stadyum, hamam ve s&uuml;tunlu cadde oluşturmaktadır. Stadyum, antik d&uuml;nyanın en iyi korunanlarından biridir.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">ASPENDOS: Antalya&#39;nın 25 mil doğusundaki ve ana yolun 3 mil uzağında yer alan&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Aspendos, T&uuml;rkiye kıyısındaki her bir yapıya rakip olan bir tiyatroyla s&uuml;slenmiştir. Aspendos İkinci y&uuml;zyılda inşa edilmiş ve 15.000 kişilik bir oturma yeri olan yapı, &uuml;st kornişin bir kısmı hari&ccedil;, neredeyse b&uuml;t&uuml;nd&uuml;r. Mimar, Xenon&#39;du ve b&ouml;yle m&uuml;kemmel bir akustik yaratmanın sırrı hen&uuml;z keşfedilmemiş yerel bir delikanlıydı.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Side Anadolu&#39;da Pamphylia b&ouml;lgesinde bulunmakta olup hem Hellenistik hem de Roma d&ouml;nemlerinde zengin bir Ege ticaret merkezi ve M&Ouml; 1. ve 2. y&uuml;zyılda Kilikya korsanları i&ccedil;in bir &uuml;s olmuştur.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">KURSUNLU ŞELALELERİ: Kurşunlu Şelaleleri, Antalya&#39;nın b&uuml;y&uuml;leyici bir milli parkı olan Antalya-Alanya karayolu boyunca 18 km uzaklıktadır.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Otelden transfer hizmeti.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Konforlu ve klimalı minib&uuml;s ve profesyonel rehberle seyahat edin</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Seyahat masrafı/sigortası dahildir.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">İ&ccedil;ecekler dahil değildir.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Giriş &Uuml;cretleri ve &Ouml;ğle Yemeği dahildir.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Antalya merkez ofisi.</span></span></p>\n', '', '8-9 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan rehber.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Turdan 24 saat &ouml;nce.</span></span></p>\n', '', 'Тур по Перге, Аспендос, Сайд ', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Это самое продаваемое развлечение в Анталии</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; 08:00 Встреча и прибытие в центральный офис Анталии Калеичи</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">08:45 Перге, 20 км к востоку от Анталии. Экскурсия по древнему городу в сопровождении гида.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">10:45 Отправление в Сиде / продолжение</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">11:15 Прибытие в Сиде и час свободного времени.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">12:15 Поход в деревню Белкис на обед.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">12:45 Перерыв на обед у реки Белкис</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">13:45 Во второй половине дня вы посетите древний театр Аспендоса и римский акведук.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">15:15 Переход к водопаду Куршунлу.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">15:45 По пути в Испарту мы посетим водопад Куршунлу и национальный парк.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">17:30 Прибытие в Анталию.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">ПЕРГЕ: Хотя руины города находятся не в масштабах Эфеса и Руины города такие же большие, как Эфес и Бергама.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Большая часть Перге состоит из Pax Romana (Roman Peace, Римский Мир) - театра, стадиона, хаммама и улицы с колоннами. Стадион является одним из наиболее хорошо сохранившихся мест в древнем мире</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">АСПЕНДОС: В 25 милях к востоку от Анталии и в 3 милях от главной дороги расположен Аспендос.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Театр на турецком побережье настолько прекрасен, что может использоваться даже в наше время.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Аспендос &ndash; это здание, построенное во втором веке и рассчитано на 15 000 человек, оно почти завершено, за исключением одной части верхнего карниза. Архитектором был Ксенон, а секретом создания такой идеальной акустики была идея местного неизвестного мальчика. Сиде расположен в регионе Памфилии в Анатолии, богатом эгейском торговом центре как в эллинистический, так и в римский периоды, а также являлся базой для киликийских пиратов в 1-м и 2-м веках до нашей эры.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">ВОДОПАДЫ КУРШУНЛУ: Водопады Куршунлу находятся в 18 км от шоссе Анталия-Алания и это место является очаровательным национальным парком Анталии.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Транспорт из отеля.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Путешествуйте комфортабельным микроавтобусом с кондиционером и профессиональным гидом</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Командировочные расходы / страховка включена.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Напитки не включены.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Входные билеты и обед включены.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Главный офис в Анталии.</span></span></p>\n', '', '9 часов', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
