(42, 'Spice Bazaar & Bosphorus Tour(Half Day Morning) ', 'Spice-Bazaar--Bosphorus-TourHalf-Day-Morning-', 'cc37e-meric-dagli-bqfmufn6xis-unsplash.jpg', 'e82b4-david-monje-fgxxdfvwsaw-unsplash.jpg', '3030', 27, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">We will pick you up from hotel (city center hotels), then you will meet with your group and guide at the meeting point. We will visit City Walls (by bus), Golden Horn (by bus), Spice Bazaar. After visiting Spice Bazaar we will cruise on Bosphorus where we will see from the sea Ciragan Palace, Ortakoy Mosque, Military High School, Rumeli Fortress. After tour we will drop you off to your hotel.<br />\n	<br />\n	Spice Bazaar, Bosphorus Tour On Boat, City Walls, Golden Horn</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">City Walls-Built by Constantine the Great, they have surrounded and protected the city of Constantinople.<br />\n	Golden Horn-It has long been a natural harbour of the city. The Horn was the favoured meeting of the sweet waters.<br />\n	Spice Bazaar (Egyptian Bazaar)-The air here is filled with the enticing aromas of cinnamon, caraway, mint, saffron.<br />\n	Bosphorus By Boat-An amazing cruise between Europe (Ortakoy) and Asia (Beylerbeyi Palace), along the Bosphorus by the Ciragan Palace, Ortakoy Mosque, Military High School, Rumeli Fortress.<br />\n	The Rumeli Fortress-Castle was built by Mehmet II to prevent the Byzantine fleet, which had control of the Bosphorus, from communicating with its northern allies.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">INCLUDED</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Hotel pick up &amp; drop off by air-conditioned non-smoking tour coaches</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Entrance fees</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Professional licensed tour guide</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Service charges &amp; local taxes</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">​<strong>EXCLUDED</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Meal, beverage</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Personal expenses</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Tips &amp; gratitues</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Pick Up Location : Hotel pick-up &amp; drop-off service are available only from the hotels located in the city center. There may be an extra charge for transportations from other locations or airport.</span></span></p>\n', '', '3-4 Hours', 0, '', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">English speaking tour guide.</span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Spice Bazaar, Bosphorus Tour On Boat, City Walls, Golden Horn</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 0, 27, 'Mısır Çarşısı ve Boğaz Turu (Yarım Gün Sabah)', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sizi otelden (şehir merkezi otelleri) alacağız, ardından buluşma noktasında grubunuzla ve rehberinizle buluşacaksınız. Surlar (otob&uuml;sle), Hali&ccedil; (otob&uuml;sle), Mısır &Ccedil;arşısı&#39;nı ziyaret edeceğiz. Mısır &Ccedil;arşısı&#39;nı ziyaret ettikten sonra, &Ccedil;ırağan Sarayı, Ortak&ouml;y Camii, Askeri Lise, Rumeli Hisarı&#39;ndan g&ouml;receğimiz Boğaz&#39;ı gezeceğiz. Turdan sonra sizi otelinize bırakacağız.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Mısır &Ccedil;arşısı, Boğazi&ccedil;i Tur Teknesi, Surlar, Hali&ccedil;</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">B&uuml;y&uuml;k Konstantin tarafından inşa edilen surlar, Konstantinopolis şehrini kuşattı ve korudu.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Hali&ccedil;-Uzun zamandır kentin doğal bir limanı olmuştur. Hali&ccedil; tatlı suların en g&ouml;zde buluşmasıydı.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Mısır &Ccedil;arşısı (Mısır &Ccedil;arşısı) -Buradaki hava, tar&ccedil;ın, kimyon, nane, safranın baştan &ccedil;ıkarıcı aromalarıyla doludur.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Boğaz teknesi ile -Avrupa (Ortak&ouml;y) ile Asya (Beylerbeyi Sarayı)arasında harika bir gezi yaparak , Boğaz boyunca &Ccedil;ırağan Sarayı, Ortak&ouml;y Camii, Askeri Lise, Rumeli Hisarı&rsquo;nı g&ouml;receksiniz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Rumeli Hisarı-Kalesi, II. Mehmet tarafından, Boğazın kontrol&uuml; altında olan Bizans filosunun kuzey m&uuml;ttefikleri ile iletişim kurmasını &ouml;nlemek i&ccedil;in inşa edilmiştir.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Otel transferi, sigara i&ccedil;ilmeyen tur otob&uuml;sleri tarafından karşılanmaktadır</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Giriş bedeli</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Profesyonel lisanslı tur rehberi</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Servis &uuml;cretleri ve yerel vergiler</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Yemek, i&ccedil;ecek</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Kişisel giderler</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bahşişler</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Teslim Alma Yeri: Otelden alma ve otele bırakma hizmeti yalnızca şehir merkezinde bulunan otellerden sağlanmaktadır. Diğer yerlerden veya havalimanından yapılan nakliyeler i&ccedil;in ek bir &uuml;cret talep edilebilir.</span></span></p>\n', '', '3-4 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan Rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 Saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '', 'Египетский базар и Босфор тур (полдня)', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Мы заберем вас из отеля (отели в центре города), затем встретимся с вашей группой и проведём на место встречи. Посетим городские стены &nbsp;(на автобусе), Халич (на автобусе). После посещения базара специй мы отправимся во дворец Чираган, мечеть Ортакой, военную среднюю школу и Румели Хисары. После тура мы отвезём вас в отель.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Египетский базар, Босфорский тур на лодке, городские стены, Халич.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Стены, построенные Константином Великим, оградили и сохранили город Константинополь.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Халич издавна был природным портом города. Халич был самым популярным собранием пресной воды.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Египетский рынок - воздух здесь полон корицы, тмина, мяты и соблазнительных ароматов шафрана.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">С Босфорской лодки - Европа (Ортакой) и Азия (дворец Бейлербей) вдоль Босфора вы увидите дворец Чираган, мечеть Ортакой, военную школу, крепость Румели.Крепость-замок Румели, она была построена Мехметом для предотвращения общения со своими северными союзниками.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Туристический автобус для некурящих из отеля отвезёт вас туда и обратно..</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Входной билет</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Профессиональный лицензированный гид</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Сервис и местные налоги</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Еда, напитки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Условия регистрации: Услуга доставки из отеля &nbsp;и в отель доступна только в отелях в центре города. Дополнительная плата может взиматься за транспортировку из других мест или из аэропорта.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(43, 'Byzantine & Ottoman Relics Tour(Full Day) ', 'Byzantine--Ottoman-Relics-TourFull-Day-', 'd6fe8-santa-sophia-istanbul-1.jpg', '02449-sultan-ahmet-mosque.jpg', '3040', 27, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">We will pick you up from the hotel (city center hotels). Then you will meet with your group and guide at the meeting point. We will visit Hippodrome, Hagia Sophia Museum, Blue Mosque, Grand Covered Bazaar, Topkapi Palace, Sultan Tombs. End of the tour we will drop you off to your hotel.<br />\n	<br />\n	Hippodrome, Hagia Sophia Museum, Blue Mosque, Grand Bazaar, Topkapi Palace, Sultan Tombs.</span></span><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Hippodrome-The center of sport activites in Constantinople, capital of the Byzantine empire, today named Sultanahmet Meydani, with its four monuments;The German Fountain of Wilhelm II, Egyptian Obelisk, Serpentine Column (Spiral column), Column of Constantine.<br />\n	Blue Mosque-Unique with its 6 minarets built in the name of Sultan Ahmet which was until 19th century traditional point for the pilgrimage to Mecca (closed on Friday).<br />\n	Hagia Sophia-The most famous Christian church in Turkey, one of the greatest marvels of architecture, which was constructed as a basilica in the 6th century by Emperor Justinian (closed on Monday).<br />\n	Grand Covered Bazaar-The most attractive shopping centre in the world, with nearly 4000 shops, selling antique, jewellery, gold, carpets, leather wear and souvenirs (closed on Sunday).<br />\n	Lunch (Drinks are extra)-You can choose kebab, pide, desert such as baklava and other delicious Turkish traditional food.<br />\n	Sultan Tombs-Tucked around the back of Hagia Sophia. There are five tombs of sultans; Sultan Selim II, Sultan Murad III, Sultan Mehmed III, Sultan Mustafa I, Sultan Ibrahim I (closed on Monday).<br />\n	Topkapi Palace-The residence of Ottoman Sultans. See the imperial treasury, sacred Islamic relics, palace kitchens, Chinese porcelain, weapons (closed on Tuesday)</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">INCLUDED</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Hotel pick up &amp; drop off by air-conditioned non-smoking tour coaches</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Lunch</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Entrance fees</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Professional licensed tour guide</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Service charges &amp; local taxe</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">EXCLUDED</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Drinks</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Personal expenses</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Tips and gratitues</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Harem part in Topkapi Palace</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Pick Up Location : Hotel pick-up &amp; drop-off service are available only from the hotels located in the city center. There may be an extra charge for transportations from other locations or airport.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">CLOSED</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Hagia Sophia Museum closed on Monday (From on October 31. to on March 31.) Replaced with Underground Cistern<br />\n	Blue Mosque closed on Friday due to Friday Prayer / No replacement<br />\n	Grand Bazaar on Sunday / Replaced with the Handicraft Store<br />\n	Topkapi Palace closed on Tuesday<br />\n	Sultan Tombs on Monday / Replaced with Little Hagia Sophia Mosque</span></span></p>\n', '8 Hours', 0, '', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">English speaking tour guide.</span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Hippodrome, Hagia Sophia Museum, Blue Mosque, Grand Bazaar, Topkapi Palace, Sultan Tombs.</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 0, 34, 'Bizans ve Osmanlı Eserleri Turu (Tam Gün)', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sizi otelden alacağız (şehir merkezi otelleri). Ardından buluşma noktasında grubunuzla ve rehberinizle buluşacaksınız. Hipodrom, Ayasofya M&uuml;zesi, Sultanahmet Camii, Kapalı &Ccedil;arşı, Topkapı Sarayı, Sultan T&uuml;rbeleri&#39;ni gezeceğiz. Tur sonunda sizi otelinize bırakacağız.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Hipodrom, Ayasofya M&uuml;zesi, Sultanahmet Camii, Kapalı &Ccedil;arşı, Topkapı Sarayı, Sultan T&uuml;rbeleri.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Hipodrom - Bizans imparatorluğunun başkenti Konstantinopolis&rsquo;te bulunan spor merkezi, g&uuml;n&uuml;m&uuml;zde Sultanahmet Meydanı olarak adlandırılan d&ouml;rt anıtıyla , II. Alman Wilhelm &Ccedil;eşmesi, Mısır Dikilitaş, Serpantin S&uuml;tun(Spiral/Yılanlı S&uuml;tun), Konstantin S&uuml;tunu.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Eşsiz 6 minareli Sultanahmet Camii Sultan Ahmet adına inşa edilmiş ve burası 19. y&uuml;zyıla kadar Mekke&#39;ye hac ziyaretinin geleneksel noktasıydı (Cuma g&uuml;n&uuml; kapalı).</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ayasofya - İmparator Justinianus tarafından 6. y&uuml;zyılda bazilika olarak inşa edilen, en b&uuml;y&uuml;k mimarlık mucizelerinden biri olan, T&uuml;rkiye&#39;nin en &uuml;nl&uuml; Hıristiyan kilisesidir (Pazartesi g&uuml;n&uuml; kapalı).</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Kapalı &Ccedil;arşı - Antik, m&uuml;cevher, altın, halı, deri giyim ve hediyelik eşya satan yaklaşık 4000 mağazasıyla d&uuml;nyanın en cazip alışveriş merkezidir (Pazar g&uuml;n&uuml; kapalı).</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ouml;ğle Yemeği (İ&ccedil;ecekler ekstradır) - Kebap, pide, baklava gibi tatlılar ve diğer geleneksel T&uuml;rk yemeklerini se&ccedil;ebilirsiniz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sultan T&uuml;rbeleri, Ayasofya&#39;nın arkasına sıkışmış durumdadır ve Beş sultanın mezarları vardır; Sultan II. Selim, III. Sultan II., III. Mehmed, III. Sultan III (Pazartesi g&uuml;n&uuml; kapalı).</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Topkapı Sarayı-Osmanlı Sultanlarının evidir. Burada İmparatorluk hazinesi, Kutsal İslam eserleri, saray mutfakları, &Ccedil;in porselenleri, silahları g&ouml;receksiniz(salı g&uuml;n&uuml; kapalı).</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><u><strong>Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</strong></u></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sigara i&ccedil;ilmeyen tur otob&uuml;sleri tarafından otelden alıp /otele bırakma.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ouml;ğle yemeği</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Giriş &uuml;creti</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Profesyonel lisanslı tur rehberi</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Servis &uuml;cretleri ve yerel vergi</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><u><strong>Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</strong></u></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">İ&ccedil;ecekler</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Kişisel giderler</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bahşişler</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Topkapı Sarayı&#39;ndaki harem b&ouml;l&uuml;m&uuml;</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Teslim Alma Yeri: Otelden alma ve otele bırakma hizmeti yalnızca şehir merkezinde bulunan otellerden sağlanmaktadır. Diğer yerlerden veya havalimanından yapılan nakliyeler i&ccedil;in ek bir &uuml;cret talep edilebilir.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">KAPALI</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ayasofya M&uuml;zesi Pazartesi g&uuml;n&uuml; kapalı (31 Ekim&#39;den 31 Mart&#39;a kadar) Yerebatan Sarnıcı ile değiştirildi</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sultanahmet Camii Cuma g&uuml;n&uuml; Cuma namazı nedeniyle kapalı</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pazar g&uuml;n&uuml; Kapalı &Ccedil;arşı / El Sanatları Mağazası ile değiştirildi</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Topkapı Sarayı Salı g&uuml;n&uuml; kapalı</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pazartesi g&uuml;n&uuml; sultan mezarları / K&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;k Ayasofya Camii ile değiştirildi</span></span></p>\n', '8 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan Rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 Saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '', 'Тур по Византийской и Османской Реликвии (на целый день)', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Мы заберём вас из отеля (отели в центре города). Затем вы встретитесь со своей группой гидом на условленом месте. Вы посетите Ипподром, музей Айя-София, Голубую Мечеть, Большой Базар, Дворец Топкапы, Гробницы Султанов. В конце тура отвезём вас в отель.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ипподром, музей Айя-София, Голубая Мечеть, Большой Базар, Дворец Топкапы, Гробницы Султанов</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ипподром, музей Айя-София, Голубая Мечеть, Большой Базар, Дворец Топкапы, Гробницы Султанов - Спортивный центр, расположенный в Константинополе, столице Византии, с его четырьмя памятниками, теперь называемыми площадью Султанахмет. Немецкий фонтан Вильгельма II, Египетский Обелиск, Змеиная Колонна (Спираль / Змеиная Колонна), Колонна Константина.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Голубая Мечеть построена в честь Cултана Ахмета уникальна своими 6 минаретами, и до 19-го века это было традиционным местом для паломников, которые отправлялись в Мекку (закрыт в пятницу).</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Собор Святой Софии (Айя-София) - построена в шестом веке императором Юстинианом, это один из крупнейших архитектурных чудес и является самой известной христианской церковью в Турции (закрыта в понедельник).</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Большой Базар - это самый привлекательный торговый центр в мире (закрыт в воскресенье), в котором около 4000 магазинов, которые продают антиквариат, ювелирные изделия, золото, ковры, кожаную одежду и сувениры.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Обед (напитки за дополнительную плату) - Вы можете выбрать такие десерты, как кебаб, лаваш, пахлава и другие традиционные турецкие блюда.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Гробницы султанов находятся за Софийским собором, и там находятся гробницы пяти султанов; Султана Селим II, Султан Мехмед III и т.д. (выходной понедельник).</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Дворец Топкапы является домом османских султанов. Здесь вы увидите императорские сокровища, священные исламские работы, дворцовые кухни, китайский фарфор, оружие (выходной - вторник).</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">&bull; Туристический автобус для некурящих из отлея отвезёт вас туда и обратно.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">&bull; Входной билет</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">&bull; Профессиональный лицензированный гид</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">&bull; Сервис и местные налоги</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">&bull; Напитки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">&bull; Гарем во дворце Топкапы</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Условия регистрации: Услуга доставки из отеля и в отель доступна только в отелях в центре города. Дополнительная плата может взиматься за транспортировку из других мест или из аэропорта.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Музей Святой Софии закрыт в понедельник (с 31 октября по 31 марта) и заменен Цистерной Базилика.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Голубая мечеть закрыта на пятничную молитву в пятницу.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">В воскресенье Большой базар заменён на Магазин Искусств.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Дворец Топкапы закрыт во вторник.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">В понедельник Гробницы Султанов заменены на мечеть Малая Айя-София.</span></span></p>\n', '8 часов', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(44, 'Ottoman Relics Tour(Half Day Afternoon)', 'Ottoman-Relics-TourHalf-Day-Afternoon', 'd2d39-sultan-tombs.jpg', '4ba89-topkapipalacetours.jpg', '3050', 27, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">We will pick you up from your hotel (city center hotels), then you will meet with your group and guide at the meeting point. We will visit Sultan Tombs and Topkapi Palace. End of the tour we will drop you off to your hotel.<br />\n	<br />\n	Sultan Tombs, Topkapi Palace</span></span><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Sultans Tombs-Tucked around the back of Hagia Sophia. There are five tombs of sultans: Sultan Selim II, Sultan Murad III, Sultan Mehmed III, Sultan Mustafa I, Sultan Ibrahim I.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Topkapi Palace-It was residence of the Ottoman sultans for almost 400 years. Palace complex consists of four main courtyards, important relics of the Muslim world, Muhamed&rsquo;s clock and sword.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Sultans Tombs closed on Monday / Replaced with Little Hagia Sophia Mosque</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Topkapi Palace closed on Tuesday</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(Harem is not included in the program and visit is due to extra entrance fee.)</span></span></div>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">INCLUDED</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Hotel pick up &amp; drop off by air-conditioned non-smoking tour coaches</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Entrance fees</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Professional licensed tour guide</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Service charges &amp; local taxes</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;EXCLUDED</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Meal, beverage</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Personal expenses</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Tips and gratitues</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p class=\"lh1em\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; line-height: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Pick Up Location : Hotel pick-up &amp; drop-off service are available only from the hotels located in the city center. There may be an extra charge for transportations from other locations or airport.</span></span></p>\n', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">CLOSED</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Topkapi Palace on Tuesday</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Sultans Tombs closed on Monday / Replaced with Little Hagia Sophia Mosque</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">IMPORTANT NOTICE</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">This tour is not operated on Tuesday.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(Harem is not included in the program and visit is due to extra entrance fee.)</span></span></div>\n', '3-4 Hours', 0, '', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">English speaking tour guide.</span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Sultans Tombs-Tucked around the back of Hagia Sophia. There are five tombs of sultans: Sultan Selim II, Sultan Murad III, Sultan Mehmed III, Sultan Mustafa I, Sultan Ibrahim I.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Topkapi Palace-It was residence of the Ottoman sultans for almost 400 years</span></span></div>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 0, 35, 'Osmanlı Kalıntıları Turu (Yarım Gün Öğleden Sonra)', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sizi otelinizden (şehir merkezi otelleri) alacağız, ardından buluşma noktasında grubunuzla ve rehberinizle buluşacaksınız. Sultan T&uuml;rbeleri ve Topkapı Sarayı&#39;nı ziyaret edeceğiz. Tur sonunda sizi otelinize bırakacağız.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sultan T&uuml;rbeleri, Topkapı Sarayı</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sultanlar Mezarları Ayasofya&#39;nın arkasına sıkışmış durumdadır. Beş padişahın mezarı vardır: Sultan II. Selim, III. Murad, III. Mehmed, I. Mustafa, I. İbrahim</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Topkapı Sarayı - Yaklaşık 400 yıldır Osmanlı padişahlarının ikametgahıydı. Saray kompleksi d&ouml;rt ana avludan, M&uuml;sl&uuml;man d&uuml;nyasının &ouml;nemli kalıntılarından, Hz. Muhammed&rsquo;in saatinden ve kılı&ccedil;larından oluşur.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Sultan Mezarları Pazartesi g&uuml;n&uuml; kapalı / K&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;k Ayasofya Camii ile değiştirildi</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Topkapı Sarayı Salı g&uuml;n&uuml; kapalı</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">(Harem programa dahil değildir ve ziyaret ilave giriş &uuml;creti gerektirmektedir.)</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\"><u><strong>Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</strong></u></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Otel, sigara i&ccedil;ilmeyen tur otob&uuml;sleri tarafından karşılanmaktadır.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Giriş bedeli</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Profesyonel lisanslı tur rehberi</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Servis &uuml;cretleri ve yerel vergiler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\"><u><strong>Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</strong></u></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Yemek, i&ccedil;ecek</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Kişisel giderler</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">İpu&ccedil;ları ve bahşişler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Teslim Alma Yeri: Otel alma ve bırakma hizmeti yalnızca şehir merkezinde bulunan otellerden sağlanmaktadır. Diğer yerlerden veya havalimanından yapılan nakliyeler i&ccedil;in ek bir &uuml;cret talep edilebilir.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">KAPALI</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Topkapı Sarayı Salı g&uuml;n&uuml; kapalı</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sultanlar Mezarları Pazartesi g&uuml;n&uuml; kapalı / K&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;k Ayasofya Camii ile değiştirildi</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ouml;NEMLİ BİLDİRİM</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bu tur Salı g&uuml;n&uuml; d&uuml;zenlenmiyor.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">(Harem programa dahil değildir ve ziyaret ilave giriş &uuml;creti gerektirmektedir.)</span></span></p>\n', '3-4 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan Rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 Saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '', 'Тур по османским руинам (пол дня)', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Мы заберем вас из отеля (отели в центре города), затем встретим вашу группу и привезём к месту встречи. Посетим гробницы Султана и Дворец Топкапы. В конце тура отвезём вас в отель.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Гробницы Султанов, Дворец Топкапы.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Гробницы султанов находятся прямо за Собором Святой Софии (Айя-София). Там находятся могилы пяти султанов: Султана Селима II, Мурада III, Мехмеда III, Мустафы I, Ибрагима I.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; Дворец Топкапы - резиденция османских султанов на протяжении почти 400 лет. Дворцовый комплекс является одним из четырех главных дворов мусульманского мира. Он состоит из часов и мечей Мухаммеда.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; Гробницы Султанов в понедельник заменены на мечеть Малая Айя София.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Дворец Топкапы закрыт во вторник</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">(Гарем не включен в программу, и его посещение осуществляется за дополнительную плату.)</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Отель, туристический автобус для некурящих из отеля отвезёт вас туда и обратно.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Входной билет</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Профессиональный лицензированный гид</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Сервис и местные налоги</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Еда, напитки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Советы и чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Условия регистрации: Услуга доставки из отеля и в отель доступна только в отелях в центре города. Дополнительная плата может взиматься за транспортировку из других мест или из аэропорта.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Дворец Топкапы закрыт во вторник</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Гробницы султанов закрыты в понедельник и заменены на мечеть Святой Софии (Айя-София)</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">ВАЖНОЕ УВЕДОМЛЕНИЕ</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Этот тур не проводится во вторник.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">(Гарем не включён в программу, и его посещение осуществляется за дополнительную плату.)</span></span></p>\n', '3-4 часа', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	За 24 часа до тура.</p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
