(56, 'Pamukkale & Laodicea Tour Full Day', 'Pamukkale--Laodicea-Tour-Full-Day', '3e15e-gymnasium-and-stadium-in-laodicea.jpg', 'dc758-zeus-temple-3.jpg', '4070', 28, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Zeus Temple, Theater, Church, Monumental Fountain, Odeon, Imperial Cult, Caracalla Fountain, Syria Avenue, Gymnasium and Stadium in Laodicea. Necropolis, Roman Baths, Domitian Gate, Latrina, Oil Factory, Frontinious Street, Agora, Byzantium Gate, Triton Fountain, Cathedral, Apollon Temple, Plutonium, Theater and Antique Pool in Pamukkale.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">We pick you up from your hotel in Karahayit or Pamukkale at a determinated time. Laodicea &amp; Pamukkale tour starts at 09:30.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">First place to visit is Laodicea antique city. You will see Zeus Temple, Theater, Church, Monumental Fountain, Odeon, Imperial Cult, Caracalla Fountain, Syria Avenue, Gymnasium and Stadium. Next you will visit the Red Water in Karahayit. The rock formations here have a reddish hue due to the components included in the spring water. This thermal water spring is considered to have healing properties. After the visit to the Red Water, you will have lunch at a local restaurant near Pamukkale. You will visit the antique city of Hierapolis after the lunch. The places to visit are Necropolis, Roman Baths, Domitian Gate, Latrina, Oil Factory, Frontinious Street, Agora, Byzantium Gate, Triton Fountain, Cathedral, Apollon Temple, Plutonium, Theater and Antique Pool. </span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Last destination of the tour is the white travertine terraces of Pamukkale. You will walk down the hill among the travertine pools. This is the best opportunity to take photos of this unique beauty of nature. The tour ends at 16:00 and you will be transferred back to your hotel in Karahayit or Pamukkale.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">INCLUDED</span></u></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Professional tour guide</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">all entrance fees</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">all transportations</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">open buffet lunch</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">EXCLUDED</span></u></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Personal expenses and tips</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Pick up from your hotel.</span></span></p>\n', '', '6-7 Hours', 0, '', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">English Speaking tour guide.</span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Zeus Temple, Theater, Church, Monumental Fountain, Odeon, Imperial Cult, Caracalla Fountain, Syria Avenue, Gymnasium and Stadium in Laodicea. Necropolis, Roman Baths, Domitian Gate, Latrina, Oil Factory, Frontinious Street, Agora, Byzantium Gate, Triton Fountain, Cathedral, Apollon Temple, Plutonium, Theater and Antique Pool in Pamukkale.&nbsp;</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '9-17', '0-8', 0, 45, 'Pamukkale ve Laodikya Turu Tam Gün', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Zeus Tapınağı, Tiyatro, Kilise, Anıtsal &Ccedil;eşme, Odeon, İmparatorluk K&uuml;lt&uuml;, Caracalla &Ccedil;eşmesi, Suriye Caddesi, Laodikya&#39;da Spor Salonu ve Stadyum. Nekropol, Roma Hamamları, Domitian Kapısı, Latrina, Petrol Fabrikası, Frontinious Caddesi, Agora, Bizans Kapısı, Triton &Ccedil;eşmesi, Katedral, Apollon Tapınağı, Pl&uuml;tonyum, Tiyatro ve Antikkale.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sizleri belirlenen saatte Karahayıt veya Pamukkale&#39;deki otelinizden alıyoruz. Laodikya ve Pamukkale turu 09:30 &#39;da başlıyor.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ziyaret edilecek ilk yer Laodikya antik kentidir. Zeus Tapınağı, Tiyatro, Kilise, Anıtsal &Ccedil;eşme, Odeon, İmparatorluk K&uuml;lt&uuml;, Caracalla &Ccedil;eşmesi, Suriye Caddesi, Spor Salonu ve Stadyumu g&ouml;receksiniz. Ardından Karahayıt&#39;taki Kırmızı Su&#39;yu ziyaret edeceksiniz. Buradaki kaya oluşumları, kaynak suyunda bulunan bileşenler nedeniyle kırmızımsı bir renk tonuna sahiptir. Bu termal su kaynağının iyileştirici &ouml;zelliklere sahip olduğu d&uuml;ş&uuml;n&uuml;lmektedir. Kızıl Su ziyaretinden sonra &ouml;ğle yemeğinizi Pamukkale yakınlarındaki yerel bir restoranda yiyeceksiniz. &Ouml;ğle yemeğinden sonra antik Hierapolis şehrini ziyaret edeceksiniz. G&ouml;r&uuml;lecek yerler Nekropolis, Roma Hamamları, Domitian Kapısı, Latrina, Petrol Fabrikası, Frontinious Caddesi, Agora, Bizans Kapısı, Triton &Ccedil;eşmesi, Katedral, Apollon Tapınağı, Pl&uuml;tonyum, Tiyatro ve Antik Havuz&#39;dur.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Turun son hedefi Pamukkale&#39;nin beyaz traverten teraslarıdır. Traverten havuzları arasında tepeden aşağıya y&uuml;r&uuml;yeceksiniz. Doğanın bu eşsiz g&uuml;zelliğinin fotoğraflarını &ccedil;ekmek i&ccedil;in en iyi fırsat. Tur saat 16: 00&#39;da bitecek ve Karahayit veya Pamukkale&#39;deki otelinize geri d&ouml;neceksiniz.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Profesyonel rehber</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">t&uuml;m giriş &uuml;cretleri</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">t&uuml;m ulaşımlar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">a&ccedil;ık b&uuml;fe &ouml;ğle yemeği</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">kişisel masraflar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">bahşişler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Otelden servis.</span></p>\n', '', '6-7 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '', 'Памуккале и Лаодикия Тур на целый день', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Храм Зевса, Театр, Церковь, Монументальный Фонтан, Одеон, Имперский Культ, Фонтан Каракаллы, Улица Сирии, Стадион Лаодикии, Некрополь, Римские Хамамы, Домицианские Ворота, Латрина, Нефтяной Завод, Улица Фронтинус, Агора, Византийские Ворота, Фонтан Тритон, Кафедральный Собор, Храм Аполлона, Плутония, Театр и Антиккале.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Мы отвезём вас из отеля в Карахаит или Памуккале в назначенное время. Тур по Лаодикии и Памуккале начинается в 09:30.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Первое место для посещения - древний город Лаодикия. Вы увидите Храм Зевса, Театр, Церковь, Монументальный Фонтан, Одеон, Имперский Культ, Фонтан Каракаллы, Сирийскую улицу, Стадион. Затем вы посетите иточник Красная Вода в Карахаите. Горные породы здесь из-за минеральных компонентов в родниковой воде имеют красноватый оттенок. Считается, что этот источник термальной воды обладает целебными свойствами. После посещения Красной воды вы пообедаете в местном ресторане возле Памуккале. После обеда посетите древний город Иераполис, Некрополь, Римские Хамамы, Домицианские ворота, Латрина, Нефтяной Завод, Улица Фронтинус, Агора, Византийские Ворота, Фонтан Тритон, Кафедральный собор, Храм Аполлона, Плутоний, Театр и Античный Бассейн.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Конечный пункт тура - белые травертиновые террасы Памуккале. Вы спуститесь с холма между травертиновыми бассейнами. Это самая лучшая возможность сфотографировать эту уникальную природную красоту. Тур заканчивается в 16:00, и вы вернётесь в свой отель в Карахаите или Памуккале.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull;Профессиональный гид</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull;Все входные билеты</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull;Весь транспорт</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull;Обед &quot;шведский стол&quot;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сервис из отеля.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(58, 'Cappadocia Turkish night ', 'Cappadocia-Turkish-night-', '292a0-turkish-night-1920x1080.jpg', 'b50cf-turkish-night-686x386.jpg', '1010', 23, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">If you are only stopping over Cappadocia for a short time you may like to pre-arrange a night out, this is a good example of what you may like to do.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Turkish Night: Experience the Turkish culture and traditional dances. There will be live music performed by a traditional custom band. Enjoy the folk dances from different parts of Turkey, Belly Dancer, Traditional Turkish Wedding Ceremony, Fire Dance. During the night the waiters will serve unlimited soft and alcoholic drinks with appetizers. The main course will be lamb with rice. The cost including transport.</span></span></p>\n', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">After booking, you will receive an email asking about which hotel you are staying in and we will give you a time of pick-up from your hotel.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">You can also&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">write your hotel information at the stage of booking.</span></div>\n', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Round-trip transfer from your hotel&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Dinner (vegetarian, chicken, fish, beef)</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Traditional shows</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverage</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick up from your hotel.</span></span></p>\n', '', '2 Hours', 0, '1', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">No need.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">24 Hours before the activity.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Traditional dances, foods, music, alcohols</span></span></p>\n', 'surekli', 0, '1', 1, '<p>\n	turkish night, dances, cultural dances</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Experience the Turkish culture and traditional dances.&nbsp;</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '12+', '6-12', '0-5', 0, 15, 'Türk Gecesi ', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Kapadokya da kısa bir s&uuml;re i&ccedil;in bulunuyor geceyi dışarda ge&ccedil;irmeyi planlıyorsanız , bu yapmak isteyeceğiniz g&uuml;zel bir aktivitedir.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">T&uuml;rk Gecesi: T&uuml;rk k&uuml;lt&uuml;r&uuml;n&uuml; ve geleneksel danslarını deneyimleyin. Geleneksel &ouml;zel grup tarafından ger&ccedil;ekleştirilen canlı m&uuml;zik olacak. T&uuml;rkiye&#39;nin farklı yerlerinden halk dansları, Oryantal Dans&ccedil;ı, Geleneksel T&uuml;rk D&uuml;ğ&uuml;n T&ouml;reni, Ateş Dansı ile eğlenin. Gece boyunca garsonlar, meze ile sınırsız alkols&uuml;z ve alkoll&uuml; i&ccedil;ecekler servis edecek. Ana yemek. Maliyete ulaşım dahildir.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ulaşım</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Akşam yemeği</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">G&ouml;steri</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Giriş &uuml;creti</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Otelden servis.</span></span></p>\n', '', '3 Saat', '<p>\n	-</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Aktiviteden 24 saat &ouml;nce.</span></span></p>\n', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Geleneksel danslar.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Geleneksel lezzetler.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Geleneksel m&uuml;zik.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', 'Турецкая Ночь Шоу ', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Если вы планируете провести интересные вечера с открытым небом в Каппадокия то это лучшее место для вас.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Шоу &laquo;Турецкая Ночь&raquo;: вы познакомитесь с турецкой культурой и традиционными танцами. Будет живая музыка в исполнении традиционной частной группы. Вы весело проведёте время наблюдая за народными танцами из разных уголков Турции, некоторые из них: танец живота, традиционная турецкая свадебная церемония и огневое шоу. Всю ночь официанты будут подавать закуски и неограниченное количество безалкогольных и алкогольных напитков. Основные блюда. Всё включено.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Транспорт</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Ужин</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Выставки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Входной билет</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Транспортный сервис из отеля.</span></span></p>\n', '', '3 часа', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до активности.</span></span></p>\n', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Традиционные танцы.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Традиционные деликатесы.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Традиционная музыка.</span></span></div>\n', 'Noche Turca', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Cappadocia tambi&eacute;n es por un per&iacute;odo corto de tiempo, si planeas pasar la noche afuera, esta es una buena opci&oacute;n de actividades que puedes hacer.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Noche turca: Experimente la cultura turca y los bailes tradicionales. Habr&aacute; m&uacute;sica en vivo interpretada por un grupo privado tradicional. bailes folcl&oacute;ricos de diferentes partes de Turqu&iacute;a, bailarina de la danza, ceremonia de boda tradicional turca, se divierten con la danza del fuego. Durante la noche, los camareros servir&aacute;n un aperitivo y un n&uacute;mero ilimitado de bebidas no alcoh&oacute;licas y alcoh&oacute;licas. Plato principal esta incluido dentro del precio.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '3 horas', '', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Bailes tradicionales.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Sabores tradicionales.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; M&uacute;sica tradicional.</span></span></p>\n'),
(59, 'Cappadocia Whirling Dervishes Ceremony', 'Cappadocia-Whirling-Dervishes-Ceremony', '4046c-dervish-ceremony-cappadocia1920x1080.jpg', '6b73b-derviches-686x386.jpg', '1020', 23, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">If you are only stopping over Cappadocia for a short time you may like to pre-arrange a sufi dance show, this is a good example of what you may like to do.</span></span></p>\n', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sema (Whirling dervishes ceremony), is the inspiration of Mevlana Celaleddin-i Rumi (1207 - 1273) as well as part of the Turkish culture, belief, and history in Konya. It symbolizes the different meanings of a mystic cycle to perfection (Ascension - Mirac). The Sema (whirling dervishes) ceremony represents all a mystical journey of man&#39;s spiritual ascent through love, finding the truth and arriving to the &quot;Perfect&quot;. Then he returns from these spiritual journeys as a man who reached maturity and a greater perfection, so as to love and to be of service to the whole creation, to all creatures without discriminating in regard to belief, class, or race.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">The Whirling Dervish Ceremony is performed at&nbsp; 6 pm each night for about 1 hour. We take you there and back for free.</span></span></div>\n', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">After booking, you will receive an email asking about which hotel you are staying in and we will give you a time of pick-up from your hotel.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">You can also write your hotel information at the stage of booking.</span></span></div>\n', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Round-trip transfer from your hotel&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">A cup of traditional soft drink.&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Traditional religious dance</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Pick up from your hotel.</span></span></p>\n', '', '1 Hour', 0, '1', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">No need.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">24 Hours before the activity.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 0, '<p>\n	dervish, semah, sema, ceremony, historical, history, mevlana,&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Whirling dervishes ceremony,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">mystical journey</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Sema (Whirling dervishes ceremony), is the inspiration of Mevlana Celaleddin-i Rumi (1207 - 1273) as well as part of the Turkish culture, belief and history in Konya.&nbsp;</span></p>\n', 1, 0, '18+', '4-17', '', 0, 46, 'Kapadokya Semazen Gösterisi', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Kapadokya da kısa bir s&uuml;re i&ccedil;in bulunuyor geceyi dışarda ge&ccedil;irmeyi planlıyorsanız , bu yapmak isteyeceğiniz g&uuml;zel bir aktivitedir.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sema (Sema derviş t&ouml;reni), Mevlana Celaleddin-i Rumi&#39;nin (1207 - 1273) ilham kaynağı olduğu gibi, Konya&#39;daki T&uuml;rk k&uuml;lt&uuml;r&uuml;n&uuml;n, inancının ve tarihinin bir par&ccedil;asıdır. Mistik bir d&ouml;ng&uuml;n&uuml;n m&uuml;kemmellikten farklı anlamlarını sembolize eder (Y&uuml;kseliş - Mirac). Sema (derviş) t&ouml;reni, insanın sevgi yoluyla, ger&ccedil;eği bulmak ve &quot;M&uuml;kemmel&quot; e ulaşmak i&ccedil;in ruhsal y&uuml;kselişinin mistik bir yolculuğunu temsil eder. Daha sonra bu manevi yolculuklardan, inan&ccedil;, sınıf ya da ırk konusunda ayrımcılığa uğramadan t&uuml;m aleme, b&uuml;t&uuml;n varlığa, sevgiye ve hizmetine sahip olmak i&ccedil;in olgunluğa ve daha m&uuml;kemmel bir m&uuml;kemmele ulaşan bir adam olarak geri d&ouml;ner.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Semazen G&ouml;sterisi her gece saat 9:00 ve 18:00 arasında 1 saat boyunca ger&ccedil;ekleştirilir. Eğer araca ihtiyacınız varsa, sizi oraya g&ouml;t&uuml;rebilir, &uuml;cretsiz olarak geri alabiliriz.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">t&uuml;m giriş &uuml;cretleri</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">t&uuml;m ulaşımlar</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Otelden servis.</span></p>\n', '', '1 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '', 'Каппадокия шоу семазен (танцующие дервиши)', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Если вы планируете провести ночь на улице в течении короткого времени, Каппадокия это хорошее время провождения.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сема (церемония дервиша Сема) является&nbsp; источником вдохновения для Мевланы Джелаледдин-и Руми (1207 - 1273), а также является частью турецкой культуры, веры и истории в Конье. Символизирует различные значения мистического цикла от совершенства (Вознесение - ночь вознесе́ния Мухаммеда). Церемония сема (дервиша) представляет собой мистическое путешествие духовного вознесения человека через любовь, чтобы найти истину и достичь &laquo;Совершенного&raquo;.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Затем духовное путешествие чтобы достичь всего мира, всех существ, любви и служения без различия на основе веры, класса или расы, чтобы достичь зрелости, совершенства, &nbsp;совершенного возвращения, к человечности.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Cемазен (танцующие дервиши)проводится каждую ночь с 9:00 до 18:00 в течение 1 часа.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Бесплатный сервис туда и обратно.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Все вступительные взносы</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Весь транспорт</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Транспортный сервис из отеля.</span></span></p>\n', '', '1 час', '<div role=\"label\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"ts-alignment-element\" data-is-focusable=\"true\" id=\"tgtAlignment_0\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\">нет</span> <span class=\"ts-alignment-element\" data-is-focusable=\"true\" id=\"tgtAlignment_1\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\">необходимости</span> <span class=\"ts-alignment-element\" data-is-focusable=\"true\" id=\"tgtAlignment_2\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\">руководство.</span></span></span></div>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до начала тура.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(60, 'Cappadocia Airport Transfer shuttle (regular)', 'Cappadocia-Airport-Transfer-shuttle-regular', 'f01ba-photography-of-airplane-during-sunrise-723240.jpg', '65045-woman-sitting-on-a-chair-inside-an-airport-3885593.jpg', '1030', 23, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Should you require transport from the airport (Kayseri Erkilet Airport (ASR) or Nevsehir Kapadokya Airport (NAV) Pick up services are round-trip available to your hotel in Cappadocia or from your Hotel in Cappadocia to Airport.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;\">The driver will be waiting you at the exit gate of the airport he will be holding a board where your name writes on. This is a regular airport transfer so there will be other guest on the bus.</span></span></p>\n', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">After booking, you will receive an email asking about which hotel you are staying in and we will give you a time of pick-up from your hotel.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">From airport to hotel booking again we will ask for flight number and hotel information on the email.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">You can also&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">write your flight details and hotel information at the stage of booking.</span></div>\n', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;\">Transportation.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;\">Parking fees.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;\">At Airport or at your hotel.</span></span></p>\n', '', '60 Minute.', 0, '1', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;\">No need.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">24 Hours before the pick up.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '', 'surekli', 0, '1', 1, '<p>\n	cappadocia transfer, airport transfer, shuttle bus, vip bus, vip car</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Should you require transport from the airport (Kayseri Erkilet Airport (ASR) or Nevsehir Kapadokya Airport (NAV) Pick up services are round-trip available to your hotel in Cappadocia or from your Hotel in Cappadocia to Airport.&nbsp;</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '3-5', 0, 11, 'Normal Kapadokya & Kayseri Havaalanı Transferi ', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Havalimanından (Kayseri Erkilet Havaalanı (ASR) veya Nevşehir Kapadokya Havaalanı (NAV)) transfer yapmanız gerekiyorsa, reservasyon aşamasında u&ccedil;uş bilgilerinizi ve otel bilgisini yazmayı unutmayın. Kapadokya&#39;daki otelinize veya Kapadokya&#39;daki otelinizden havalimanına gidiş d&ouml;n&uuml;ş m&uuml;mk&uuml;nd&uuml;r.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">S&uuml;r&uuml;c&uuml; sizi havaalanının &ccedil;ıkış kapısında bekliyor olacak ve adınızın yazdığı bir pankart tutuyor olacak. Bu d&uuml;zenli bir havalimanı transferi olduğundan otob&uuml;ste başka misafirlerde olacaktır.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Transfer</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Park &uuml;cretleri</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Havaalanından alış veya otelinizden alış.</span></span></p>\n', '', '1,5 Saat', '<p>\n	-</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Transfer hizmetinden 24 saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '', 'Трансфер из аэропорта Каппадокии (регулярный)', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Если вам требуется трансфер из аэропорта (Kayseri Erkilet Airport (ASR) или Nevsehir Kapadokya Airport (NAV)), пожалуйста, не забудьте указать данные вашего рейса и название отеля на этапе бронирования. Услуги трансфера в оба конца доступны для вашего отеля в Каппадокии или из вашего отеля в Каппадокии до аэропорта.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Водитель будет ждать вас у выхода из аэропорта, он будет держать доску, на которой написано ваше имя. Это регулярный трансфер из аэропорта, поэтому в автобусе будет другой гость.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Перевозка</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Стоимость парковки</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Встреча в аэропорту или транспорт из вашего отеля.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '', '1 час', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до услуги трансфера.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
