(136, 'Turkey Tour Package based on 10 Days', 'Turkey-Tour-Package-based-on-10-Days', '10b20-e389cef479fc0f26fff024ed14a4540d-1-.jpg', '59bcb-824f6-galata-tower.jpg', '15082019', 32, '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Best of Turkey 10 days</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Day 1 &ndash;Istanbul</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Day 2 &ndash; Sultanahmet &ndash; Old Istanbul (B)</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Day 3 - Bosphorus Cruise with St. (Haghia) Sophia &amp; Beylerbeyi (B)</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Day 4 - Istanbul- Cappadocia (B)</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Day 5 - Cappadocia (B)</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Day 6- Cappadocia &ndash; Konya &ndash;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Pamukkale (B)</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Day 7 &ndash;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Pamukkale (B)</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Day 8 &ndash; Ephesus (B)&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Day 9 &ndash;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Istanbul &ndash; (B)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1. Day:&nbsp;Arrival in Istanbul</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Welcome to Istanbul the magnificient city that brought all different nations and cultures together history long.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Our representatives will meet you and drive you to your hotel. Check in your hotel and meet our guide at the lobby to have info-giving meeting for your Must to see places in Turkey Tour.<br />\n	We wish to keep rest of the day at your leisure but please note that we are available anytime you want to do to something.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Tomorrow we will have our Istanbul&rsquo;s highlights tour, you are kindly requested to be ready at lobby at mentioned time by our guide.<br />\n	Overnight stay at hotel.</span></span></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n	<hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" />\n</div>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">2. Day:&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">(Breakfast-Lunch)<br />\n	Good Morning. Your tour guide and driver are at lobby to take you for your Istanbul&rsquo;s Higlights Tour.<br />\n	Today&rsquo;s programme will start by visiting the ancient Hippdrome where you will get to know all details of its transformation, obelisks and fonctions during history.<br />\n	The Hippodrome is hand by hand with World wide famous Blue Mosque so we will be entering to Blue Mosque after our Hippodrome Tour.<br />\n	Sultanahmet is named by it&rsquo;s visitors as Blue Mosque because of the magnificient tiles and breath-taking decoration inside. You will have a fully guided tour here.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">The next stop is Hagia Sophia, which one of the must to see places in World but not only in Turkey. The whole story and history of the Hagia Sophia churh-mosque-museum will be presented by your guide.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Your guide will take you for a lunch in a very good local restaurant. Here you will have the chance to talk and make critics about your tour and some rest for next visiting place The Underground Basilica Cistern. Which was the water-warehouse for Roman&rsquo;s &amp; Ottoman&rsquo;s Istanbul.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">The driver will pick you up after your fully guided Cisterna Tour and take you to your hotel.<br />\n	We wish you a nice and comfortable night.<br />\n	Please note that you will have some free time tomorrow untill your domestic flight to one of the most important place is list of must to see in Turkey; Cappadocia.<br />\n	Overnight stay at hotel.</span></span></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n	<hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" />\n</div>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">3. Day:&nbsp;From Istanbul to Cappadocia by Plane &amp; Overnight Cave Hotel in Cappadocia</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">(Breakfast )<br />\n	Good morning!<br />\n	Your guide and driver will take you to airport for your flight to Cappadocia. On your arrival our agents will meet you and take you to your hotel and give you information about your tour programme in Cappadocia.<br />\n	<br />\n	You will have time to rest at your hotel, if you wish to have a Turkish night dinner or visiting the whirling dervishes show our agents will be very helpful to you.<br />\n	<br />\n	Your hotel is carefully selected and it is a unique cave hotel.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">We wish you a nice and comfortable night and looking forward to meeting you tomorrow morning for an unforgetable Cappadocia Tour.<br />\n	During your tour you will be visiting, Goreme Open air museum, Rock Churches, Uchisar Castle, Rock Castle, Cavusin Old Greece Village, Pasabagı Fairy Chimneys, Avanos Pottery Demonstrations, Devrent Imagination Valley, &Uuml;rg&uuml;p Wine Tasting.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Enjoy the comfort and hospitality at your hotel.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Recommended activity for tonight:</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"http://www.blueeyetour.com/Tour/detail/Cappadocia-Turkish-night-\">Turkish Night</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.blueeyetour.com/Tour/detail/Cappadocia-Whirling-Dervishes-Ceremony\">Whirling Dervishes Ceremony</a>&nbsp;with Dinner 45 Euro Per Person</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Recommended activity for tomorrow:</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"http://www.blueeyetour.com/Category/detail/Hot-Air-Balloon-Flights\">Hot Air Balloon Flight</a>&nbsp;at Sunrise in Cappadocia for 180 Euro</span></span></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n	<hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" />\n</div>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">4. Day:&nbsp;Cappadocia&rsquo;s Highlights Tour 1</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">(Breakfast &ndash; Lunch)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n	Good morning!<br />\n	Your guide and driver will be waiting for you after you had breakfast.<br />\n	Today is the day to explore must to see places in Cappadocia. The tour will cover Goreme Open air museum,Rock Churches, Uchisar Castle, Rock Castle, Cavusin Old Greece Village, Pasabagı Fairy Chimneys, Avanos Pottery Demonstrations, Devren Imagination Valley, Urg&uuml;p Wine Tasting.<br />\n	You will have lunch in a very good local restaurant by having a break on your tour.<br />\n	After the tour we will take you back to your hotel. We wish you a nice and comfortable night.<br />\n	Overnight stay at hotel&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n	<hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" />\n</div>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">5. Day:&nbsp;Cappadocia&rsquo;s Highlights Tour 2</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">(Breakfast &ndash; Lunch)<br />\n	Good morning!<br />\n	Cappadocia is more than we have seen yesterday so we are having our second Cappadocia tour today by visiting Goreme Panorama, Derinkuyu Underground City, Ihlara Valley, Belisırma Village, Selime Monastery, Uchisar Pigeon Valley,</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Today we will have our lunch in another restaurant to taste another dish from Turkish cuisine because visiting a country is not only about sightseeing. We provide you a large experience from history to cuisine of this country.<br />\n	After the tour we will take you back to your hotel. We wish you a nice and comfortable night.<br />\n	Overnight stay at hotel&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n	<hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" />\n</div>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">6. Day:&nbsp;From Cappadocia to Ephesus by Plane</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">(Breakfast &ndash; Lunch)</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Good morning!<br />\n	Now its the day to say good bye to beautiful Cappadocia and start our journey to one of the other must of seeing the ancient city of Ephesus and unique cotton castle of Pamukkale. And not only that we will also be visitin Virgin Mary&rsquo;s House.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Your flight from Cappadocia to Izmir is arranged. You will be transferred to airport by our agents. On your arrival to Izmir you will meet our agents from our Ephesus- Pamukkale Office.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Rest of the day in Kusadasi,&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n	<hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" />\n</div>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">7. Day:&nbsp;Virgin Mary House And Ephesus Tour</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">(Breakfast &ndash; Lunch)</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Today is the time for a marble white , history long and holy land tour. One of the best preserved ancient cities on the world : Ephesus and it&rsquo;s most important guest Virgin Mary&rsquo;s house are the destination for the tour.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">This daily Ephesus tour will be one of the top points of your travels and also one of the Ancient Wonders will get a place in your photo albums.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">After the Ephesus tour you will visit the house that Virgin Mary spent her last years in.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Then you will be transferred to Pamukkale the city of Cotton Castle.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Overnight in Pamukkale</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Note. Next day Following Optional Tours are Available:</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sunrise Hot Air Balloon Flight in Pamukkale</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Horse Riding Tours in Pamukkale</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Paragliding Above Pamukkale</span></span></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n	<hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" />\n</div>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">8. Day:&nbsp;Hierapolis &amp; Pamukkale Tour</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">(Breakfast &ndash; Lunch)</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">A bright morning for the world&rsquo;s only cotton caste Pamukkale. Which is happened after warm tears of the nature, as if the beauty of the white pearl on Cleopatra&rsquo;s chest was the inspiration for this art work of the nature.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Today you will see the ancient city of Hierapolis and Cleopatra&rsquo;s private swimming pool and also walk in calcium rich warm pools of Pamukkale.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">After the tour you will have time to enjoy the thermal therapy at your hotel.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Transfer to your hotel and free time at your leisure.</span></span></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n	<hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" />\n</div>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">9. Day:&nbsp;Flight From Denizli to İstanbul &amp; Afternoon Bosphorus Cruise Tour</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Good morning!</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">This morning you will be transferred to Denizli airport for your flight to Istanbul.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">On arrival transfer from Istanbul airport to your hotel.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">You have had an amazing time during your tour and now we want you to celebrate it in between two continents and on beatiful water and shores of Boshporus.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bosphorus is the river which divides Istanbul in two parts : Asia &ndash; Europe. This makes Istanbul one of the most important cities in the world to be based in two continents.<br />\n	Bosphorus is actually a panoramic summary of history and art in Istanbul. The houses, palaces, pavilions and gardens on shores will give you a great feeling.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">You will be visiting Istanbul&rsquo;s highest peak Camlica Hill and have your lunch there. After your tour we will take you to your hotel.Overnight</span></span></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n	<hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" />\n</div>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">10. Day:&nbsp;Packing Day</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">(Breakfast )</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">The 10 Days we have had spent with you gives us a big pleasure, we hope you liked our tours, services, staff and friendship.<br />\n	We definitely want you to keep us in mind and tell good stories to your friends and families about Blue Eye Travel.</span></span></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n	<hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" />\n</div>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Thank you very much for travelling with Blue Eye Tour.</span></span></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n	<hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" />\n</div>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', '<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:15.0pt;margin-left:\n0cm\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">What Price Includes</span></strong></span></span><o:p></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:15.0pt;margin-left:\n0cm\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">Transfers<br />\n	&bull; Return airport transfers in Istanbul<br />\n	&bull; Return airport transfers in Cappadocia (Kayseri)<br />\n	&bull; Return airport 