ns-serif;\">&bull; Алтарь и Каменный стол</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; 3000-летний неиссякаемый водоисточник</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Руины Римских хамамов - здание театра</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Южные ворота и руины</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Свободное время на обед</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Древний театр Ассос</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Мост Хюдавендигар</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Мечеть Хюдавендигар</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Водяные Цистерны</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Римские Башни</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Посещение деревни Бехрамкале</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; 18:00 Конец тура.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">08:00 Отправление в Трою</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Илион или Троя (хеттский язык: Вилуса (Vilusa) или Тревиза &nbsp;(Truvisa), греческий: &Tau;&rho;&omicron;ί&alpha; [Troia] или Ί&lambda;&iota;&omicron;&nu; [İlion], латынь: Troia или Ilium) &ndash; это исторический город на окраине горы Ида (древняя гора Ида), в провинции Чанаккале. Это древний город, где в Илиаде произошла Троянская война, один из двух стихов, который, как считается, был написан Гомеросом. В 1870 г. немецкий археолог-любитель Генрих Шлиман обнаружил недалеко от&nbsp; села Тевфикие древнейший античныйгород. На сегодняшний день большую часть экспанатов археологических раскопок этого города находится в Турции, Германии и России. Древний город включен в список Всемирного Наследия с 1998 года, а в Национальный Парк - с 1996 года.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Древний город расположен на &laquo;Холме Хисарлык&raquo; к западу от деревни Тевфикие центрального района Чанаккале (39&deg;58&prime;K, 26&deg;13&prime;D). Холм размером 200х150м и высотой 31,2м состоит из слоёв известниковых пород .</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Долгое время не было известно, что холм Хисарлык был древним городом, пока не были найдены археологические раскопки и останки в этом районе. Когда город Троя был основан, холм Хисарчик был местом, где ручьи Карамендерес и Дюмрек Чай вливались в море. Благодаря раскопкам известно, что эти ручьи раньше&nbsp; были на много ближе к проливу Чанаккале (Дарданеллы).</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Исторический район города, который называется Троя (или Троад), находится сегодня на азиатском континенте провинции Чанаккале.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Боги и богини - Небольшое руководство</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ахиллес - греческий герой, бессмертный, кроме Ахеллесовой Пяты</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Гектор - троянский герой, мастер с копьём и мечом</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Хелен &ndash; ярость и гнев войны</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Париж - любовник Хелены, старый пастух, чудовище.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Король Приам - Отец Гектора и Парижа</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Аякс - еще один греческий герой</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Новое A / C транспортное средство</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Профессиональный туркоязычный гид</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Обед</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Напитки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Дополнительная плата гиду и водителю</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сервис из отеля.</span></span></p>\n', '', '9-10 часов', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(78, 'Çanakkale Daily Gallipoli Tour', 'canakkale-Daily-Gallipoli-Tour', 'a18ed-gallipoli-2.jpg', 'c9863-gallipoli-1.jpg', '5120', 33, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Visiting:</strong></span></span></p>\n<ol>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Brighton Beach,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Beach Cemetery,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">ANZAC Cove,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ariburnu Cemetery,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">ANZAC Commemorative Site,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Respect to Mehmetcik Statue,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Lone Pine Australian Memorial,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Johnston&#39;s Jolly, (Turkish and Allied trenches and tunnels),</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Turkish 57. Infantry Regiment Cemetery,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">The Nek,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Chunuk Bair New Zealand Memorial.</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>The Gallipoli battlefields</strong>&nbsp;are on the&nbsp;<strong>Gallipoli</strong>&nbsp;(Gelibolu)&nbsp;<strong>Peninsula</strong>, away from any towns or villages. There are no shops on the tour route so kit yourself with whatever you need beforehand. A snack box and toilet stop are part of the tour.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>The Gallipoli battlefields</strong>&nbsp;are actually quite a long way from the town of Gallipoli (nowadays &#39;Gelibolu&#39;) that gave its name to the peninsula, and hence the campaign. &Ccedil;anakkale is therefore a more logical place to stay, offering more in the way of facilities and things to do when not on the tour. &Ccedil;anakkale is a real Turkish town, not a tourist resort, with a fairly active cultural and social life.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Staying outside &Ccedil;anakkale still means that you can join the tour. We are flexible enough to accommodate visitors from nearby locations and pick them up before we head off to the battlefields.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">A check list for your day pack might include: Film and camera, hat and/or sun screen if you&#39;re sensitive to the sun (we&#39;ll be outside much of the time and shade is sometimes scarce), and sensible footwear - we&#39;ll be walking along earth tracks part of the way.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">The tour is conducted at a leisurely pace. We do not rush you round. There will be time to stroll on your own, take photos, pay respects, and, if you&rsquo;re lucky, find some relics.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">It is not possible to include Cape Helles on this tour. However, all-day&nbsp;<strong>Gallipoli Tours</strong>&nbsp;can be arranged according to numbers, or privately, which include Cape Helles and Suvla Bay, the other two battle fronts.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Questions</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">If the weather is bad? We still go, and adapt to the conditions.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Do the tours run all year? The number of visitors tends to drop off in the winter months but if there are enough of you, yes, we go!</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Can I visit Gallipoli and Troy the same day? If you take an organised tour to Troy it&rsquo;s possible. If you try to do it independently, you may arrive there after the site has closed.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Transportation in A/C &#39;NO - SMOKING&#39; coach from Istanbul to Eceabat &amp; Eceabat to Istanbul,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Breakfast on the way,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Fully Guided Gallipoli tour,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Professional English speaking guide,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Restaurant lunch in Eceabat during Gallipoli Tour,&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick up from your hotel.</span></span></p>\n', '', '8-9 Hours', 0, '1', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">English speaking guide</span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<strong style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The Gallipoli battlefields</strong><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;are on the&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Gallipoli</strong><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;(Gelibolu)&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Peninsula</strong><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">, away from any towns or villages. There are no shops on the tour route so kit yourself with whatever you need beforehand. A snack box and toilet stop are part of the tour.</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 0, 49, 'Çanakkale Şehitlik Turu', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">TARİHİ GELİBOLU YARIMADASI ŞEHİTLİKLERİ&nbsp; TURU</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ziyaret Programı</span></span></div>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ccedil;anakkale merkez alınış noktalarından &uuml;cretsiz transfer,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ccedil;anakkale&rsquo;den hareket,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Avrupa yakası Eceabat/Kilitbahir&rsquo;e varış,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bigalı K&ouml;y&uuml; ve Atat&uuml;rk&uuml;n karagah olarak kullandığı ev,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Anzak Koyu ve &ccedil;ıkarmanın yapılışı,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Mehmet&ccedil;iğe Saygı Anıtı,Kanlı Sırt,Kırmızı Sırt ve Merkeztepe muharebelerinin anlatılması,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Conkbayırı Muharebeleri, siperler ve Mustafa Kemal&rsquo;in saatinin par&ccedil;alandığı yer,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ouml;ğle yemeği</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Şehitler Abidesi,Camlı Şehitlik,T&ouml;ren Alanı tanıtımı ve fotoğraf &ccedil;ekimi,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Morto Koyu,Sedd&uuml;lbahir k&ouml;y&uuml;,&Ouml;zel M&uuml;ze ziyareti (&uuml;cerete dahil)</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Yahya &Ccedil;avuş anıtı,Ertuğrul koyu,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Şahindere Şehitliği ve ger&ccedil;ek mezarlıkların ziyaret edilmesi,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Seyit onbaş anıtı,Rumeli ve Namazgah tabyaları,Kilitbahir kalesi,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ccedil;anakkale&rsquo;ye Hareket</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ccedil;anakkale&rsquo;ye varış,</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ccedil;anakkale merkez bırakış noktalarına &uuml;cretsiz transfer,</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Şehitlik Turumuz &Ccedil;anakkale Hareketli olup, diğer hareket noktalarından katılan m&uuml;ştrilerimiz de saat 09:15&#39;de Şehitlik gezimizin başlayacağı nokta olan &Ccedil;anakkale Saat Kulesi Meydanında &Ccedil;anakkale ofisin&#39;de buluşuyoruz, 10.00 feribotu ile Avrupa yakasındaki Tarihi Gelibolu Yarımadası&#39;na ge&ccedil;iyoruz. İlk durağımız Bigalı k&ouml;y&uuml; daha sonra&nbsp; Arıburnu ve Anzakların &ccedil;ıkarma yaptığı koyu ziyaret edip, Hemen ardından Mehmet&ccedil;iğe Saygı Anıtı ve Kanlı Sırt b&ouml;lgesini ara&ccedil;ta anlatarak, 57. Alay Şehitliğine gidiyoruz. Atat&uuml;rk&#39;&uuml;n g&ouml;zetleme yeri, saatinin par&ccedil;alandığı yer,siperlerin ve Yeni Zellanda anıt ve mezarlıklarınında de bulunduğu Conkbayırı&#39;nı g&ouml;rd&uuml;kten sonra &ouml;ğle yemeği i&ccedil;in mola veriyoruz.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Yemekten sonra turumuzun &ouml;ğleden sonraki kısmında; Şehitler Abidesi, Morto Koyu, ara&ccedil;tan Panoramik Fransız anıtı, Sedd&uuml;lbahir K&ouml;y&uuml;, Sedd&uuml;lbahirdeki &Ouml;zel 1915 Savaş Malzemeleri M&uuml;zesini ve Yahya &Ccedil;avuş Anıtını ve şehitliğini ziyaret ediyoruz. Rehberimiz &ccedil;ıkartma muharebelerini ve İngilizlerin River Clyde gemisinden Truva atına benzer &ccedil;ıkartmasına T&uuml;rk askerinin muhteşem savunmasını anlatıyor, daha sonra Şahindere Hastane şehitliğine ge&ccedil;iyoruz, buradaki bozulmadan kalan gercek şehitlik ve mezarları ziyaret ettikten sonra dillere destan Seyit onbaşı hikayesini seyit onbaşı anıtında dinliyoruz, akabinde Mecidiye ve Namazgah tabyalarının ziyareti ve Kilitbahir kalesinin anlatımlarından sonra turumuz Avrupa yakasında sona eriyor. Anadolu Yakasına ge&ccedil;ecek olan m&uuml;şterilerimiz 18:00 feribotu ile &Ccedil;anakkale&#39;ye ge&ccedil;iyor.</span></span></div>\n', '', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Modern A / C ara&ccedil;larıyla ulaşım</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Otelden transfer</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Profesyonel t&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan rehber</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">&Ouml;ğle yemeği&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Kişisel giderler</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">İ&ccedil;ecekler</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">S&uuml;r&uuml;c&uuml; ve rehbere isteğe bağlı bahşişler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Oteden servis.</span></span></p>\n', '', '8-9 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan Rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 Saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
