(81, 'Fethiye Paragliding', 'Fethiye-Paragliding', 'c6b1b-paragliding-04.jpg', 'f0f14-paragliding-03jpg.jpg', '6110', 37, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Experience the thrill of flying over Oludeniz, the undisputed paradise for paragliding in Turkey! Launching from the top of Babadag Mountain, you&rsquo;ll have panoramic views of the renowned Blue Lagoon, Butterfly Valley, unspoiled coves, and picturesque scenery around this famous coastal town.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">From all around the world, people flock to&nbsp;<strong>Oludeniz</strong>&nbsp;for the chance to go paragliding because it&rsquo;s home to&nbsp;<strong>one of the highest commercial launch sites in the world</strong>! Combined with the absolutely stunning views from above, you will have a unique paragliding adventure flying in tandem with your licensed pilot at an altitude of&nbsp;<strong>1,700 meters</strong>. Highlights from your flight include:<br />\n	<br />\n	- Blue Lagoon (Oludeniz beach)<br />\n	- Butterfly Valley<br />\n	- Cyprus Island<br />\n	- The 12 islands of Gocek Bay &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Your launch point is from the summit of&nbsp;<strong>Babadag</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>Fethiye&#39;s highest mountain</strong>that&rsquo;s situated just a couple of kilometers away from the coast. Before the flight, you&rsquo;ll have a briefing about the take-off and landing process from your pilot.&nbsp;<strong>Safety first</strong>, it&rsquo;s necessary to wear a helmet during these two important parts, but during the flight, your helmet can be taken off.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">As you take to the skies, you&rsquo;ll have stunning views of Oludeniz&rsquo;s lush hills and mountains, white-sand beaches, and clear, turquoise blue waters that will leave you in awe. After&nbsp;<strong>30-40 minutes</strong>, your flight will end with you soaring over the pristine beach before making a soft landing in a designated area on the beach boardwalk.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Nearly anyone can participate in this safe and exciting paragliding flight above Oludeniz! No previous experience is necessary, and even children&nbsp;<strong>as young as 8 years old</strong>&nbsp;can join in on the fun. For couples or two people who are looking to fly together, your pilot can even organize a &ldquo;parallel flight&rdquo; where two pilots try to fly as close as possible to each other.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">For your next holiday, see for yourself why Oludeniz is legendary for paragliding flights! Take off and experience an unforgettable adventure. &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">minimum 8 y/o</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Starting time will be informed by email.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Cancellation policy:&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">24 Hours before the paragliding.</span><br />\n	<br />\n	<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Offer Description</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Your flight is approximately 30-40 minutes.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Activity requirements</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Participants must weight less than 110 kg.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Special terms</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">ilmed This activity could be canceled or postponed due to weather conditions.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Oludeniz is located approximately 200 kilometers away from Marmaris. You will be transferred to the starting point in a comfortable minibus.&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pickup times may vary in Icmeler and Turunc.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">In mid-October, the International Paragliding Festival is held in Oludeniz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">At your request, photos and a video of your flight&nbsp;are available. Please contact your instructor after booking for further information.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>INCLUDED</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pickup/Drop-off</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">30-min flight</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Transfers</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">EXCLUDED</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pictures &amp; Video</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick up from your hotel.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\"><strong>To bring</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Sunglasses</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Comfortable clothing</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Comfortable shoes</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', 'Flight 30-40 minutes', 0, '1', '1', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">English speaking guide.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">24 Hours before the paragliding.</span></span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Experience the thrill of flying over Oludeniz, the undisputed paradise for paragliding in Turkey! Launching from the top of Babadag Mountain, you&rsquo;ll have panoramic views of the renowned Blue Lagoon, Butterfly Valley, unspoiled coves, and picturesque scenery around this famous coastal town.</span></span></p>\n', 1, 0, '18+', '8-17', '', 0, 12, 'Fethiye Paraşüt', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">T&uuml;rkiye&#39;de yama&ccedil; paraş&uuml;t&uuml; i&ccedil;in tartışmasız bir cennet olan &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz&#39;e u&ccedil;manın heyecanını yaşayın! Babadağ Dağı&#39;nın tepesinden &ccedil;ıkarak, &uuml;nl&uuml; Mavi Lag&uuml;n&#39;&uuml;n, Kelebekler Vadisi&#39;nin, bozulmamış koyların ve bu &uuml;nl&uuml; sahil kasabası &ccedil;evresindeki pitoresk manzaraların panoramik manzaralarına hayran kalcaksınız.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">D&uuml;nyanın her yerinden insanlar, yama&ccedil; paraş&uuml;t&uuml; yapma şansı i&ccedil;in &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz&#39;e akın ediyor &ccedil;&uuml;nk&uuml; d&uuml;nyanın en y&uuml;ksek atlama noktalarından birine ev sahipliği yapıyor! Yukarıdan kesinlikle &ccedil;arpıcı manzaralarla birleştiğinde, lisanslı pilotunuzla birlikte 1.700 metre y&uuml;kseklikte u&ccedil;an eşsiz bir yama&ccedil; paraş&uuml;t&uuml; macerasına sahip olacaksınız.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;U&ccedil;uşunuzda &ouml;ne &ccedil;ıkanlar :</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">- Mavi Lag&uuml;n (&Ouml;l&uuml;deniz Plajı)</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">- Kelebekler Vadisi</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">- Kıbrıs Adası</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">- G&ouml;cek Koyu&#39;ndaki 12 ada</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Atlama noktanız, Fethiye&#39;nin kıyıdan sadece birka&ccedil; kilometre uzakta bulunan en y&uuml;ksek dağı olan Babadağ&#39;ın zirvesinden olacak. U&ccedil;uştan &ouml;nce, pilotunuzdan kalkış ve iniş işlemleri hakkında bir bilgi alacaksınız. &Ouml;nce g&uuml;venlik ! Kalkış ve iniş sırasında kask takmanız gerekiyor ama u&ccedil;uş sırasında kaskınızı &ccedil;ıkarabilirsiniz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">G&ouml;ky&uuml;z&uuml;ne &ccedil;ıktığınızda, &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz&#39;in yemyeşil tepelerin ve dağların, beyaz kumlu plajların ve berrak, turkuaz mavi suların &ccedil;arpıcı manzaralarına hayran kalacaksınız. 30-40 dakika sonra u&ccedil;uşunuz, sahildeki belirlenmiş bir alana yumuşak bir iniş yapmadan &ouml;nce kumsal &uuml;zerinde y&uuml;kselecek.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Hemen hemen herkes &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz&#39;in &uuml;st&uuml;ndeki bu g&uuml;venli ve heyecan verici yama&ccedil; paraş&uuml;t&uuml; u&ccedil;uşuna katılabilir! Daha &ouml;nce hi&ccedil;bir deneyime gerek yok ve eğlenceye 8 yaşındaki k&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;k &ccedil;ocuklar bile katılabilir. Beraber u&ccedil;mak isteyen &ccedil;iftler veya iki kişi i&ccedil;in, pilotunuz iki pilotun birbirine olabildiğince yakın u&ccedil;maya &ccedil;alıştığı bir &ldquo;paralel u&ccedil;uş&rdquo; d&uuml;zenleyebilir.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bir sonraki tatiliniz i&ccedil;in, &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz&#39;in yama&ccedil; paraş&uuml;t&uuml; u&ccedil;uşlarında neden efsanevi olduğunu kendiniz g&ouml;r&uuml;n! Kalk ve unutulmaz bir maceraya atıl.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">En az 8 yaş olması gerekiyor.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Başlangı&ccedil; ​​saatini size e-maille bildireceğiz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">İptal politikası:</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Yama&ccedil; paraş&uuml;t&uuml;nden 24 saat &ouml;nce.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Teklif A&ccedil;ıklaması</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">U&ccedil;uşunuz yaklaşık 30-40 dakika.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Etkinlik gereksinimleri</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Katılımcıların ağırlığı 110 kg&#39;dan daha az olmalıdır.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ouml;zel terimler</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bu aktivite, hava koşulları nedeniyle iptal edilebilir veya ertelenebilir.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ouml;l&uuml;deniz, Marmaris&#39;ten yaklaşık 200 kilometre uzaklıktadır. Konforlu bir minib&uuml;sle başlangı&ccedil; noktasına transfer edileceksiniz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Alış saatleri İ&ccedil;meler ve Turun&ccedil;&#39;ta değişebilir.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ekim ayının ortalarında, Uluslararası Yama&ccedil; Paraş&uuml;t&uuml; Festivali &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz&#39;de d&uuml;zenlenmektedir.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">İsteğiniz &uuml;zerine fotoğraflar ve u&ccedil;uşunuzla ilgili bir video sunulabilir. Daha fazla bilgi i&ccedil;in l&uuml;tfen rezervasyondan sonra eğitmeninize başvurunuz.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Otelden alma / otele bırakma</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">30 dakikalık u&ccedil;uş</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Transferler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Resimler ve Video</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Otelden servis.</span></p>\n', '', 'Uçuş 30-40 Dakika', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan pilot.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Yama&ccedil; paraş&uuml;t&uuml;nden 24 saat &ouml;nce.</span></span></p>\n', '', 'Парашют Фетхие', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Вам предоставится возможность испытать острые ощущения полёта в Турции, окунитесь в рай Мёртвого моря! С вершины горы Бабадаг вы сможете полюбоваться панорамным видом на знаменитую Голубую Лагуну, долину бабочек, нетронутые бухты и живописные пейзажи вокруг этого знаменитого приморского города.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Люди со всего мира приежают к Мёртвому морю, чтобы спуститься на параплане, потому что он является домом для одной из самых высоких точек прыжков в мире! В сочетании с совершенно потрясающими видами сверху у вас будет уникальное приключение на параплане на высоте 1700 футов в сопровождении лицензированного пилота.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; Во время полёта вы увидите:</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">- Голубую Лагуну (Пляж Мёртвого моря)</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">- Долину бабочек</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">- остров Кипр</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">- 12 островов в заливе Гёджек</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Точкой вашего прыжка станет вершина Бабадаг, самой высокой горы в Фетхие, всего в нескольких километрах от побережья. Перед полётом вы получите информацию о взлётах и посадках от вашего пилота. Безопасность прежде всего! Вам нужно надеть шлем во время взлета и посадки, но вы можете снять шлем во время полёта.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Во время полёта вы насладитесь потрясающим видом на зелёные холмы и горы Мёртвого моря, белые песчаные пляжи и чистые бирюзово-голубые воды. Через 30-40 минут вы подниметесь над пляжем, прежде чем совершить мягкую посадку в специально отведённом для этого месте на пляже.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Почти каждый может принять участие в этом безопасном и захватывающем полёте на параплане над Мёртвым морем! Для этого вам не нужен опыт, и даже маленькие дети в возрасте 8 лет могут насладиться полётом. Для пар или двух человек, которые хотят летать вместе, ваш пилот может организовать &laquo;параллельный рейс&raquo;, в котором два пилота стараются лететь как можно ближе друг к другу.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Подумайте и решите, почему Мёртвое море является сказочным полётом на параплане для вашего следующего отпуска! Вставай и отправляйся в незабываемое приключение.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Тебе должно быть не менее чем 8 лет. Мы сообщим вам о времени начала по электронной почте.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Описание предложения</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ваш полёт занимает около 30-40 минут.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Требования:</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Вес участников должен быть менее 110 кг.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Особые условия:</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Полёт может быть отменён или отложен из-за погодных условий.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Мёртвое море находится примерно в 200 километрах от Мармариса. Вы будете доставлены в назначенное место комфортабельным микроавтобусом.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Часы приёма в Ичмелер и Турунч могут отличаться.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">В середине октября на Мёртвом море проходит международный фестиваль парапланеризма.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Фотографии и видео вашего полёта могут быть сделаны по запросу. Для получения дополнительной информации, пожалуйста, свяжитесь с вашим инструктором после бронирования.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Транспрот в отель и обратно</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; 30-минутный полёт</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Трансферы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Фотографии и видео</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сервис из отеля.</span></span></p>\n', '', 'Полёт 30-40 минут', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">англоговорящий пилот</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">За 24 часа до полёта на параплане.</span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
