amily:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Профессиональный гид</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Транспорт</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Топливо</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Стоимость парковки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Не включены в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Еда и напитки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Сервис из отеля.</span></p>\n', '', '13 часов', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до начала тур</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(99, 'Green Bursa Tour (From Istanbul)', 'Green-Bursa-Tour-From-Istanbul', 'e177a-green-bursa-day-tour-from-istanbul-4.jpg', '90d38-green-bursa-day-tour-from-istanbul-1.jpg', '11110', 42, '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt 19.85pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">Green Bursa tour&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">covers the<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">&nbsp;</strong>Cable Car to Uludag, Green Tombs (Yeşil T&uuml;rbe), Olympos Mountain (Uludag), 600 years old Pine Tree.</span></span></span></p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">08:15 - 08:45 AM&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">Green Bursa Tour departs from hotel in Istanbul with pick up service.</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">The hotel pick up service for the daily istanbul tours change according to hotel location between&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">07:45 - 08:15 AM.</strong></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt 19.85pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">Green Bursa tour&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">covers the<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">&nbsp;</strong>Cable Car to Uludag, Green Tombs (Yeşil T&uuml;rbe), Olympos Mountain (Uludag), 600 years old Pine Tree.</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt 19.85pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">For Bursa Tour, travel by car ferry to Yalova, and enjoy the sea and land view of&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">Istanbul</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">Asian</strong>&nbsp;side. (The most famous thing to do during the journey is feeding the seagull by&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">simit</strong>(Kind of bread wiith sesame on it)). Arrival to Yalova continue to Bursa by coach.</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt 19.85pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">During the Bursa Tour, there will be visiting the Green Tomb (<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">Yesil T&uuml;rbe</strong>). Continue to Uludag where you will use the cable car to climb upto mountain of&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">Olympos by Cable Car</strong>.</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt 19.85pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">First stage cable car is 1.235 m</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">. Arrival to first stage of cable car and continue to have barbecue lunch in mountain. After lunch drive up to top of the mountain by coach and you will have free time on top of the mountain, in your free time you can hire an ATV and you can make&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">mountain safari</strong>&nbsp;(During the winter you can hire a ski motor and skiing From December to April). After leisure on top of mountain drive down back to Istanbul. On the way, we have a stopover in&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">600 years old Plane Tree</strong>&nbsp;and have rest there. After having rest under the pine tree.</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;line-height:200%;\nfont-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt 19.85pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">Late evening return from Bursa to Istanbul.</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">The hotel drop off service for the daily istanbul tours change according to hotel location between&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">22:00 - 23:00</strong>&nbsp;PM.</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">22:00 - 23:00</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">PM</strong>&nbsp;Arrive to hotel, after the green bursa tour.</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-fami