(102, 'Bursa Ottoman Village Tour', 'Bursa-Ottoman-Village-Tour', 'ab965-ottoman-village-tour-6.jpg', '74961-ottoman-village-tour-1.jpg', '11140', 42, '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">Ottoman Village Tour</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">&nbsp;is a daily tour which has departure everyday in Bursa, If you stay in the city of Bursa and want to make a cultural day tour to Ottoman Villages from your hotel in Bursa. The Ottoman Village tour is available everyday that you can join to historical tour to experience of the Ottoman village life style.</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">09:30 AM You will be picked up from your hotel for the&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">Ottoman Village Tour</strong>&nbsp;in Bursa.</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;line-height:\n200%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-fami