(107, 'Daily Ayder Tour', 'Daily-Ayder-Tour', '8a2ac-ayder-yaylasi2.jpg', '5620f-ayder-yaylasi2.jpg', '12150', 43, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The beautiful places that you will see with this tour&nbsp;S&uuml;rmene Knife Rayon, Rize Botanical Tea Garden, Rize Cloth Workplace, Fırtınadere Rafting Facility, Stone Bridges, Gelin T&uuml;l&uuml; Waterfall.</span></span></p>\n', '<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.45pt;margin-left:\n0cm\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">For being away from crowded of city and find peace we set out from our agency everyday at 9 o&rsquo;clock. Our first stop is in S&uuml;rmene Knife Rayon. In this rayon you can get information and about S&uuml;rmene Knives and you can buy some knives. Our second stop is in Botanical Tea Garden in Rize. You can drink tea and take photos in there. We stop by Rize Cloth Workplace and see regional loom in this workplace then we get back on the road. After 20 minutes we arrive Fırtına Valley and give a break for taking photo. Then we go to Historical Stone Bridge .After the break in Historical Stone Bridge we arrive Ayder Plato. In Gelin T&uuml;l&uuml; Waterfall you will have your free time. At 5 o&rsquo;clock we set out for returning Trabzon and complete our tour.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.45pt;margin-left:\n0cm\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Beauties:</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	&bull; Ayder is a wonderful place with its riot of color in autumn, white snow cover in winter and greenery view in summer.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	&bull; Ayder is a village, plato and entertainment place.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	&bull; With its touristic hostels, trout restaurants, small resort type hotels and nature. Ayder is a wonderful place for accommodation and travel.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	&bull;It is almost anytime possible to see people who play horon with bigpipes.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">Details:</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	The road of Ayder is 165 km for total. It takes 4 hours with breaks.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">Visit Places:</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	1- S&uuml;rmene Knife Rayon<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	2- Rize Botanical Tea Garden<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	3- Rize Cloth Workplace<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	4- Fırtınadere Rafting Facility<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	5-Stone Bridges<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	6-Gelin T&uuml;l&uuml; Waterfall</span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">PS1:&nbsp;Our tour vehicles will arranged according to the number of attendee with vehicles of 15-29- 46.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	PS2:&nbsp;Our daily tours departure time is certain.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	PS3:&nbsp;There is no insurance for place of seat (window, hall, etc.).<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	PS4:&nbsp;It is not state the brand or model of vehicle. The agency can make change when it is necessary.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	PS5: Employee in charge has right to make changes on program flow depending upon weather or road condition.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.45pt;margin-left:\n0cm\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Advices:</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	*Comfortable walking shoes or sneakers should be preferred.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	*We advices you to buy worldwide known S&uuml;rmene Knives.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	*Taste the tea when we visit Botanical Tea Factory.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	*Try Ayder&rsquo;s regional food ( muhlama, trout, laz b&ouml;reği, etc.)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	*If you love taking photos be sure that your camera is with you.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<div>\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">INCLUDED</span></span></strong></span></div>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Transportation with comfortable luxury vehicles during the tour.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Vehicle entrance to the national parks.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">In car cartering</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Seat insurance</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">EXCLUDED</span></span></strong></span></div>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Lunch</span></span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Museum entrance fee</span></span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Private expenses</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick up from your hotel.</span></span></span></p>\n', '', '8-9 Hours', 0, '1', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">English speaking tour guide.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The beautiful places that you will see with this tour&nbsp;S&uuml;rmene Knife Rayon, Rize Botanical Tea Garden, Rize Cloth Workplace, Fırtınadere Rafting Facility, Stone Bridges, Gelin T&uuml;l&uuml; Waterfall.</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 0, 70, 'Ayder Turu', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Doğa ile i&ccedil; i&ccedil;e şehrin kalabalığından uzaklaşıp , suyun duruluğu ile huzura kavuşmak , mutluluk , eğlence ve sakinlik gibi duyguların hep&nbsp; bir arada yaşanılabileceği şekilde d&uuml;zenlenmiş muhteşem bir tur</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">09:00 te ofisimizin &ouml;n&uuml;nden hareket ediyoruz. İlk durağımız S&uuml;rmene il&ccedil;esindeki y&ouml;resel S&uuml;rmene bı&ccedil;ağı reyonu. Burada S&uuml;rmene bı&ccedil;ağını tanıyıp alış verişimizi yaptıktan sonra yolumuza devam ediyoruz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bir sonraki duragımız Rizedeki Botanik &ccedil;ay bah&ccedil;esi. Burada &ccedil;ayınızı i&ccedil;ip,fotoğraf &ccedil;ekebilirsiniz..Ardından yine Rizede bulunan Rize bezi at&ouml;lyesine uğruyoruz.Y&ouml;resel dokuma tezgahlarını g&ouml;r&uuml;p,alışverişimizi yaptıkdan sonra yolumuza devam ediyoruz. </span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Yaklaşık 20dk devam ettikden sonra Fırtına vadisine varıyoruz.Fırtına deresi &uuml;zerinde bulunan rafting tesisine uğrayıp fotoğraf molası veriyoruz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bir sonraki mola yerımız olan Tarihi Taş k&ouml;pr&uuml;lerde verilen molamız sonrasında Ayder yaylasına varıyoruz.Gelin t&uuml;l&uuml; şelalesinde fotoğraf &ccedil;ekimi sonrasında serbest zaman veriyoruz. Saatimiz 17:00&rsquo;ı g&ouml;sterdiğinde&nbsp; Trabzona doğru yola &ccedil;ıkıyor ve turumuzu bitiriyoruz.</span></span></p>\n', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ziyaret Yerleri:</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1- S&uuml;rmene Bı&ccedil;ağı Reyonu</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">2- Rize botanik &ccedil;ay bah&ccedil;esi</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">3- Rize bezi at&ouml;lyesi</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">4- Rafting tesisi</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">5-Taş k&ouml;pr&uuml;ler</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">6-Gelin t&uuml;l&uuml; şelalesi</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Not 1: Tur ara&ccedil;larımız, katılımcı sayısına g&ouml;re ayarlanacak olup, 15 &ndash; 29 &ndash; 46 kişilik tur ara&ccedil;ları ile yapılacaktır.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Not 2: G&uuml;n&uuml;birlik turlarımız, kesin kalkışlıdır.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Not 3: Ara&ccedil; yerleşme planında sağ, sol veya koridor, cam kenarı garantisi ve koltuk garantisi verilmez.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Not 4: Ara&ccedil; marka ve model belirtilmez. Acente gerektiğinde ara&ccedil; değişikliği yapabilir.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Not 5:G&ouml;revli personelimiz program akışında hava ve yol durumuna g&ouml;re değişiklik yapma hakkına sahiptir.</span></span></div>\n', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Modern A / C ara&ccedil;larıyla ulaşım</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Profesyonel t&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan rehber</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Kişisel giderler</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">T&uuml;m giriş &uuml;cretleri</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">&Ouml;ğle yemeği&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">İ&ccedil;ecekler</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">S&uuml;r&uuml;c&uuml; ve rehbere isteğe bağlı bahşişler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Ofis &ouml;n&uuml;nden servis 09.00.</span></p>\n', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Gezi s&uuml;resince rahat y&uuml;r&uuml;y&uuml;ş ayakkabısı ve ya spor ayakkabı tercih edilmelidir.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">D&uuml;nyaca &uuml;nl&uuml; S&uuml;rmene bı&ccedil;aklarından almanızı tavsiye ederiz.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ziyaretini yapacağımız Botanik &ccedil;ay bah&ccedil;esinde &ccedil;ayın tadına mutlaka bakın.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ayder yaylasının y&ouml;resel tadlarını deneyin.(muhlama,alabalık,laz b&ouml;reği vb.)</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Fotoğraf merakı olanlar makinalarını mutlaka yanlarında bulundursun.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '8 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan Rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 Saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sonbaharda renk c&uuml;mb&uuml;ş&uuml;,Kışın ağa&ccedil; ve dağ eteklerini s&uuml;sleyen beyaz kar &ouml;rt&uuml;s&uuml;,yazın b&uuml;t&uuml;n sıcaklıgını bulabılecegınız muhteşem bır doğa.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ayder bir k&ouml;y, yayla ve eğlence yeridir.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Turistik pansiyonları, alabalık lokantaları, k&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;k resort tipi otelleri ve doğal manzarası ile, az bulunur g&uuml;zellikte gezi ve konaklama yeridir.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Heran tulumla horon oynayan insanları g&ouml;rmek m&uuml;mk&uuml;nd&uuml;r.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Detaylar: Ayder yolumuz toplamda 165 km olup, vereceğimiz molalarla beraber yaklaşık 4 saat s&uuml;rmektedir.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', 'Тур по Айдеру', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Тур по Айдеру</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Замечательный тур, организованный таким образом, что чувства счастья, веселья и спокойствия могут гармонировать вместе, убегая от городской толпы к природе и обретая мир.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Мы начнём экскурсию возле офиса в 09:00. Наша первая остановка &ndash; региональное отделение, где продаются ножи национальной марки Сюрмене &laquo;S&uuml;rmene&raquo; в городе Сюрмене. Здесь мы продолжим наше путешествие, познакомившись с ножами Сюрмене и сделаем покупки.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Наша следующая остановка - ботанический чайный сад Ризе. Здесь вы можете выпить чаю, сфотографироваться, а затем отправимся в тканевую мастерскую, расположенную в городе Ризе.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Пройдя около 20 минут, мы прибудем в долину Фыртына.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">После перерыва на исторических каменных мостах мы прибудем на плато Айдер. В 17:00, мы отправляемся в Трабзон и заканчиваем наш тур.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Места посещения:</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1- Региональное отделение по продаже ножей марки Сюрмене &laquo;S&uuml;rmene&raquo;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">2- Ботанический чайный сад Ризе</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">3- Тканевая мастерская Ризе</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">4- Место проведения рафтинга</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">5- Каменные мосты</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">6- Водопад Гелин Тюлю</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Примечание 1: Наши туристические транспортные средства будут предоставлены в соответствии с количеством туристов с количеством мест от 15 до 29 - 46 человек.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Примечание 2: дневные туры обязательно состоятся.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Примечание 3: мы не предоставляем услугу выбора места в автобусе.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Примечание 4: Марка и модель автомобиля не указаны. Наш агент может изменить автомобиль при необходимости.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Примечание 5: Наши сотрудники имеют право изменять курс программы в зависимости от погоды и дорожных условий.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Современные A / C транспортное средство</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Профессиональный Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Все входные билеты</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Обед</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Напитки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Дополнительные чаевые для водителя и гида</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сервис возле офиса в 09:00.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Во время поездки желательно обуть повседневную обувь для ходьбы или кроссовки.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Мы рекомендуем вам обязательно купить всемирно известные ножи марки Сюрмене &laquo;S&uuml;rmene&raquo;.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Посещая ботанический сад, обязательно выпейте горячую чашечку чая.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Попробуйте местные вкусности на плато Айдер (мухлама, форель, лазский пирог и т. Д.).</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Те, кто интересуется фотографией, не забудьте взять фотоаппарат.</span></span></p>\n', '8-9 часов', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Осенью деревья становятся красочными, зимний белый снег покрывает горы, а летом там чудесная природа и прохладный воздух.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Айдер - деревня, плато и место развлечений.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Это отличное путешествие и жилье с ресторанами форели, небольшими отелями и живописными видами.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Здесь можно увидеть людей, танцующих в комбинезонах&nbsp; хорон.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Детали: Наша дорога в Айдер составляет в общей сложности 165 км и длится около 4 часов со всеми перерывами.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(108, 'Daily Uzungol Tour', 'Daily-Uzungol-Tour', 'a721b-uzungoel-2.jpeg', '45f05-uzungoel-2.jpg', '12160', 43, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);\">The beautiful places that you will see with this tour&nbsp;</span>Uzung&ouml;l, S&uuml;rmene Knife Rayon, Tea Factory, Historical Kiremitli Bridge, Artificial waterfalls.</span></span></p>\n', '<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.45pt;margin-left:\n0cm\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">For being away from crowded of city and find peace we set out in front of our agency at 10 o&rsquo;clock. Our first stop is in S&uuml;rmene Knife Rayon. In this rayon you can get information about S&uuml;rmene Knives and you can buy some knives. Our second stop is in tea factory which located in Of district. In tea factory you will be informed about how tea comes from field to fork. You can taste the tea which is treated to you. Then we take a photography break in Historical Kiremitli Bridge and artificial waterfalls. After these breaks we arrive Uzung&ouml;l. In Uzung&ouml;l you have free time. In this time you can have lunch, go for walk, rent a bicycle and you can shop from local stores. At 5 p.m. we return for Trabzon and we ending our tour.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.45pt;margin-left:\n0cm\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Beauties:</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	&bull; Uzung&ouml;l is a wonderful place with its riot of color in autumn, white snow cover in winter and greenery view in summer.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	&bull; Uzung&ouml;l is a village, plato and entertainment place.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	&bull; With its touristic hostels, trout restaurants, small resort type hotels and nature. Uzung&ouml;l is a wonderful place for accommodation and travel.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">Details:</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	The road to Uzung&ouml;l is 99 km for total. It takes 3 hours with breaks.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">Visiting Places:</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	1- S&uuml;rmene Knife Rayon<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	2- Tea Factory<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	3- Historical Kiremitli Bridge<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	4- Artificial waterfalls</span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">PS1:&nbsp;Our tour vehicles will arranged according to the number of attendee with vehicles of 15-29- 46.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	PS2:&nbsp;Our daily tours departure time is certain.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	PS3:&nbsp;There is no insurance for place of seat (window, hall, etc.).<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	PS4:&nbsp;It is not state the brand or model of vehicle. The agency can make change when it is necessary.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" />\n	PS5: Employee in charge has right to make changes on program flow depending upon weather or road condition.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Advices:</strong><br />\n	*Comfortable walking shoes or sneakers should be preferred.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">*We advices you to buy worldwide known S&uuml;rmene Knives.<br />\n	*Taste the tea when we visit tea factory.<br />\n	*Try Uzung&ouml;l&rsquo;s regional food (muhlama , trout ,etc.)<br />\n	*If you love taking photos be sure that your camera is with you.</span></span><br />\n	&nbsp;</div>\n', '<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>INCLUDED</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Transportation with comfortable luxury vehicles during the tour.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Vehicle entrance to the national parks.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">In car cartering</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Tea treat in tea factory</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Seat insurance</span></span><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>EXCLUDED</b></span></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Lunch</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Museum entrance fee</span></span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Private expenses</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Pick up from your hotel.</span></p>\n', '', '8-9 Hours', 0, '1', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">English speaking tour guide.</span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);\">The beautiful places that you will see with this tour&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Uzung&ouml;l, S&uuml;rmene Knife Rayon, Tea Factory, Historical Kiremitli Bridge, Artificial waterfalls.</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 0, 71, 'Uzungöl Turu', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Doğa ile i&ccedil; i&ccedil;e şehrin kalabalığından uzaklaşıp , suyun duruluğu ile huzura kavuşmak , mutluluk , eğlence ve sakinlik gibi duyguların hep&nbsp; bir arada yaşanılabileceği şekilde d&uuml;zenlenmiş muhteşem bir tur.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">10:00 da ofisimizin &ouml;n&uuml;nden hareket ediyoruz. İlk durağımız S&uuml;rmene il&ccedil;esindeki y&ouml;resel S&uuml;rmene bı&ccedil;ağı reyonu. Burada S&uuml;rmene bı&ccedil;ağını tanıyıp alış verişimizi yaptıktan sonra yolumuza devam ediyoruz. </span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bir sonraki durağımız Of il&ccedil;esindeki &ccedil;ay fabrikası.Burada &ccedil;ayın bah&ccedil;eden soframıza geliş ser&uuml;venini &ouml;ğrenip,İkram edilen &ccedil;ayımızı i&ccedil;ip alışveriş yapabilirsiniz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ardından tarihi kiremitli k&ouml;pr&uuml;de ve yapay şelalelerde fotoğraf molası verip Uzung&ouml;l&rsquo;e varıyoruz. G&ouml;l kenarında bulunan restoranlar b&ouml;lgesinde&nbsp; serbest zaman veriyoruz. </span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bu s&uuml;re zarfında dileyen yemek yiyebilir,g&ouml;l etrafında y&uuml;r&uuml;y&uuml;ş yapabilir, bisiklet kiralayabilir ve ya y&ouml;resel alış veriş gibi bir &ccedil;ok aktivite den faydalanabilir. Saatimiz 17:00 g&ouml;sterdiğinde&nbsp; Trabzon&rsquo;a doğru yola &ccedil;ıkıyor ve turumuzu bitiriyoruz.</span></span></p>\n', '<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ziyaret Yerleri:</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1- S&uuml;rmene Bı&ccedil;ağı Reyonu</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">2- &Ccedil;ay Fabrikası</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">3- Tarihi Kiremitli K&ouml;pr&uuml; (Hapsiyaş)</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">4- Yapay Şelaleler</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Not 1: Tur ara&ccedil;larımız, katılımcı sayısına g&ouml;re ayarlanacak olup, 15 &ndash; 29 &ndash; 46 kişilik tur ara&ccedil;ları ile yapılacaktır.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Not 2: G&uuml;n&uuml;birlik turlarımız, kesin kalkışlıdır.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Not 3: Ara&ccedil; yerleşme planında sağ, sol veya koridor, cam kenarı garantisi ve koltuk garantisi verilmez.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Not 4: Ara&ccedil; marka ve model belirtilmez. Acente gerektiğinde ara&ccedil; değişikliği yapabilir.</span></span></div>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Not 5:G&ouml;revli personelimiz program akışında hava ve yol durumuna g&ouml;re değişiklik yapma hakkına sahiptir.</span></span></div>\n', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Modern A / C ara&ccedil;larıyla ulaşım</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Profesyonel t&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan rehber</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Kişisel giderler</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">T&uuml;m giriş &uuml;cretleri</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">&Ouml;ğle yemeği&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">İ&ccedil;ecekler</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">S&uuml;r&uuml;c&uuml; ve rehbere isteğe bağlı bahşişler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Ofis &ouml;n&uuml;nden servis 08.00.</span></p>\n', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Gezi s&uuml;resince rahat y&uuml;r&uuml;y&uuml;ş ayakkabısı ve ya spor ayakkabı tercih edilmelidir.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">D&uuml;nyaca &uuml;nl&uuml; S&uuml;rmene bı&ccedil;aklarından almanızı tavsiye ederiz.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ziyaretini yapacağımız &ccedil;ay fabrikasında &ccedil;ayın tadına mutlaka bakın.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Uzung&ouml;l&rsquo;&uuml;n y&ouml;resel tadlarını deneyin.(muhlama,alabalık vb.)</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Fotoğraf merakı olanlar makinalarını mutlaka yanlarında bulundursun.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '7 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan Rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 Saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sonbaharda renk c&uuml;mb&uuml;ş&uuml;,Kışın ağa&ccedil; ve dağ eteklerini s&uuml;sleyen beyaz kar &ouml;rt&uuml;s&uuml;, yazın b&uuml;t&uuml;n sıcaklıgını bulabılecegınız muhteşem bır doğa.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Uzung&ouml;l bir k&ouml;y, yayla ve eğlence yeridir.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Turistik pansiyonları, alabalık lokantaları, k&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;k resort tipi otelleri ve doğal manzarası ile, az bulunur g&uuml;zellikte gezi ve konaklama yeridir.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', 'Тур по Узунгёль', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Этот тур организован таким образом, чтобы вы убежали от толп города и смогли воссоединиться с природой, ощутить счастье, веселье и спокойствие.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Мы начнём экскурсию возле офиса в 09:00. Наша первая остановка &ndash; региональное отделение, где продаются ножи национальной марки Сюрмене &laquo;S&uuml;rmene&raquo; в городе Сюрмене. Здесь мы продолжим наше путешествие, познакомившись с ножами Сюрмене и сделаем покупки.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Наша следующая остановка - чайная фабрика. Здесь вы можете узнать как чай появился на столе и сможете выпить наш чай и сделать покупки.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Затем мы делаем фото-перерыв на историческом плиточном мосту и искусственных водопадах, а затем прибудем в Узунгёль. У вас будет свободное время около ресторанов на берегу озера.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">В то же время вы можете перекусить, прогуляться по озеру, взять напрокат велосипед и воспользоваться многими видами деятельности, такими как местные покупки. В 17:00 мы отправимся в Трабзон и закончим наш тур.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Места посещения:</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1- Региональное отделение по продаже ножей марки Сюрмене &laquo;S&uuml;rmene&raquo;.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">2- Чайная фабрика</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">3- Исторический плиточный мост</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">4- Искусственные водопады</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Примечание 1: Наши туристические транспортные средства будут предоставлены в соответствии с количеством туристов с количеством мест от 15 до 29 - 46 человек.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Примечание 2: дневные туры обязательно состоятся.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Примечание 3: мы паредоставляем услугу выбора места в автобусе.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Примечание 4: Марка и модель автомобиля не указаны. Наш агент может изменить автомобиль при необходимости.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Примечание 5: Наши сотрудники имеют право изменять курс программы в зависимости от погоды и дорожных условий.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Современные A / C транспортное средство</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Профессиональный Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Все входные билеты</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Обед</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Напитки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Дополнительные чаевые для водителя и гида</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сервис возле офиса в 08:00</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Во время поездки желательно обуть повседневную обувь для ходьбы или кроссовки.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Мы рекомендуем вам обязательно купить всемирно известные ножи марки Сюрмене &laquo;S&uuml;rmene&raquo;.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Посещая чайную фабрику, обязательно выпейте горячую чашечку чая.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Попробуйте местные вкусности в Узунгёле (мухлама, форель, и т. д.).</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Те, кто интересуется фотографией, не забудьте взять фотоаппарат.</span></span></p>\n', '8-9 часов', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Осенью деревья становятся красочными, зимний белый снег покрывает горы, а летом там чудесная природа и прохладный воздух.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Узунгёль - деревня, плато и место развлечений.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Это отличное путешествие и жилье с ресторанами форели, небольшими отелями и живописными видами.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `acente_tur` (`id`, `adi`, `seo_adi`, `resim`, `resim_2`, `kod`, `kat_id`, `aciklama`, `tam_aciklama`, `gezi_rehberi`, `dahil_olanlar`, `bulusma_noktasi`, `gitmeden`, `sure`, `hizli_giris`, `cok_satan`, `tukenme`, `kupon`, `hizli_onay`, `rehber`, `engelli`, `iptal`, `ayni_gun_engel`, `one_cikanlar`, `tur_donemi`, `odeme_turu`, `sticker`, `durum`, `anahtar`, `kisa_aciklama`, `cocuk_fiyat_gorunsun`, `bebek_fiyat_gorunsun`, `yetiskin_fiyat_yazisi`, `cocuk_fiyat_yazisi`, `bebek_fiyat_yazisi`, `baz_alinacak_fiyatlama_sekli`, `sorting`, `adi_tr`, `aciklama_tr`, `tam_aciklama_tr`, `gezi_rehberi_tr`, `dahil_olanlar_tr`, `bulusma_noktasi_tr`, `gitmeden_tr`, `sure_tr`, `rehber_tr`, `iptal_tr`, `one_cikanlar_tr`, `adi_ru`, `aciklama_ru`, `tam_aciklama_ru`, `gezi_rehberi_ru`, `dahil_olanlar_ru`, `bulusma_noktasi_ru`, `gitmeden_ru`, `sure_ru`, `rehber_ru`, `iptal_ru`, `one_cikanlar_ru`, `adi_esp`, `aciklama_esp`, `tam_aciklama_esp`, `gezi_rehberi_esp`, `dahil_olanlar_esp`, `bulusma_noktasi_esp`, `gitmeden_esp`, `sure_esp`, `rehber_esp`, `iptal_esp`, `one_cikanlar_esp`) VALUES
(109, '2 Days Safranbolu Amasra Tour From İstanbul', '2-Days-Safranbolu-Amasra-Tour-From-istanbul', '62524-amasra-3.jpg', 'bbd94-amasra-2.jpg', '13110', 44, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">HIGHLIGHTS: &bull; Safranbolu &bull; Cinci Turkish Bath &bull; Clock Tower &bull; Bakizadeler Mansion &bull; Arasta Bazaar &bull; Cinci Hodja House &bull; Amasra</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>DEPARTURE FROM ISTANBUL:</strong>&nbsp;Shuttle from Sultanahmet around 22:30 to the bus station where you will get the overnight public bus from Istanbul to Safranbolu around 23:59. The road takes about 7 hours.<br />\n	<br />\n	<strong>DAY 1 -&nbsp;GOLF CART SIGHTSEEING TOUR IN SAFRANBOLU</strong><br />\n	Pick up from Safranbolu bus station to old town of Safranbolu. You can join our Golf cart sightseeing tour anytime in the day; it takes about one hour and a half. We will drive through the narrow streets and stop at some important places (old wooden houses, bazaars, hamams, squares, mosque, etc) to take photos and get some information about them. We will see Cinci Turkish bath, Clock Tower, Arasta Bazaar, Bakizadeler Mansion, Topcu Bridge, Cinci Hodja House, the old government building, blacksmiths bazaar during the tour. Free time for the rest of the day.<br />\n	<br />\n	Accommodation in a historical Ottoman house in Safranbolu<br />\n	<br />\n	<strong>DAY 2 - AMASRA TOUR (B, L)</strong><br />\n	Meeting at our office in Safranbolu around 10:00am. Today, we will drive toward the Black Sea coast to visit Amasra. We will visit the museum before lunch. After having lunch at a fish restaurant, we will continue our tour seeing the Roman Castle and Walls, wood-carving handicraft bazaar, and outer and inner piers of the city. Return to Safranbolu around 17:00.<br />\n	<br />\n	Overnight public bus to Istanbul around 23:59. The road takes about 7 hours (if you will not return to Istanbul, we can arrange bus from Safranbolu to any other cities in Turkey).<br />\n	<br />\n	<strong>ARRIVAL TO ISTANBUL:</strong>&nbsp;You will arrive to Istanbul main bus station early in the morning. You will have your own way to your hotel or airport.&nbsp;<br />\n	<br />\n	<strong>END OF OUR SERVICE</strong><br />\n	<br />\n	Safranbolu is in the&nbsp;UNESCO World Heritage List.</span></span><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>NOTES</strong><br />\n	&bull; Please ask for a single supplement.<br />\n	&bull; Hotels are based on bed and breakfast. Check in time is 14:00 and check out time is 11:00.<br />\n	&bull; All tours are regular. Please contact us for private tour options.<br />\n	&bull; You can make any changes on the programme, if our programs are not suitable for you. We can work together on your itinerary.<br />\n	&bull; Programmes may change due to bad weather conditions.</span></span><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>INCLUDED</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Round trip overnight public bus tickets from/to Istanbul</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1 night accommodation</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1 golf cart sightseeing tour</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1 daily city tour</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1 breakfast</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1 lunch</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">entrance fees</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">all local transportations</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">professional guides</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<br />\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>EXCLUDED:&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Drinks at lunch</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">personal expenses</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick up from your hotel or airport in İstanbul.</span></span></p>\n', '', '2 Days', 0, '1', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">English speaking tour guide.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></span></p>\n', 1, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Safranbolu</span></b><span style=\"line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;is a town boasting a glorious collection of old Ottoman-Turkish houses, with a rich collection of art masterpieces which represent the traditional Turkish life and culture.</span></span></span></p>\n', 'surekli', 0, '1', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Safranbolu &bull; Cinci Turkish Bath &bull; Clock Tower &bull; Bakizadeler Mansion &bull; Arasta Bazaar &bull; Cinci Hodja House &bull; Amasra</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '3-17', '0-2', 0, 72, 'İstanbul\'dan 2 Gün Safranbolu Amasra Turu', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ouml;NE &Ccedil;IKANLAR : &bull; Safranbolu &bull; Cinci Hamam &bull; Saat Kulesi &bull; Bakizadeler Konağı &bull; Arasta &Ccedil;arşısı &bull; Cinci Hoca Evi &bull; Amasra</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">İSTANBUL&#39;DAN KALKIŞ: Sizi Sultanahmet&#39;ten saat 22: 30&#39;da servisle alıp terminale ge&ccedil;eceğiz. Gece 23: 59&#39;da İstanbul&#39;dan Safranbolu&#39;ya giden otob&uuml;se bineceğiz. Yolumuz yaklaşık 7 saat s&uuml;recektir.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1. G&Uuml;N - SAFRANBOLU&#39;DA GOLF ARABASI İLE GEZİ TURU</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sizi Safranbolu otob&uuml;s terminalinden alıp Safranbolu kasabasına ge&ccedil;eceğiz. Golf arabası gezi turumuza g&uuml;n&uuml;n her saati katılabilirsiniz; yaklaşık bir bu&ccedil;uk saat s&uuml;rer. Dar sokaklarda gezeceğiz ve fotoğraf &ccedil;ekmek ve onlar hakkında bilgi edinmek i&ccedil;in bazı &ouml;nemli yerlerde (eski ahşap evler, &ccedil;arşılar, hamamlar, meydanlar, cami vb.) duracağız. Tur sırasında Cinci Hamamı, Saat Kulesi, Arasta &Ccedil;arşısı, Bakizadeler Konağı, Top&ccedil;u K&ouml;pr&uuml;s&uuml;, Cinci Hoca Evi, eski h&uuml;k&uuml;met binası, demirci &ccedil;arşısını g&ouml;receğiz. G&uuml;n&uuml;n geri kalanı i&ccedil;in boş zamanımız olacak.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Safranbolu&#39;da tarihi bir Osmanlı evinde konaklayacağız.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">2. G&Uuml;N - AMASRA TURU (B, L)</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sabah saat 10.00 civarında Safranbolu&#39;daki ofisimizde buluşacağız. Bug&uuml;n Amasra&#39;yı ziyaret etmek i&ccedil;in Karadeniz kıyılarına doğru ilerleyeceğiz. &Ouml;ğle yemeğinden &ouml;nce m&uuml;zeyi ziyaret edeceğiz. Bir balık lokantasında &ouml;ğle yemeğinden sonra turumuza Roma Kalesi ve duvarları, ağa&ccedil; oymacılığı el sanatları pazarını ve şehrin dış ve i&ccedil; iskelelerini g&ouml;rmeye devam edeceğiz. Saat 17:00 civarında Safranbolu&#39;ya d&ouml;neceğiz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Gece 23:59&#39;da İstanbul&#39;a giden otob&uuml;se bineceksiniz. Yol yaklaşık 7 saat s&uuml;r&uuml;yor (İstanbul&#39;a d&ouml;nmeyecekseniz, Safranbolu&#39;dan T&uuml;rkiye&#39;nin diğer şehirlerine otob&uuml;s ayarlayabiliriz).</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">İSTANBUL&#39;A VARIŞ: Sabah erkenden İstanbul otob&uuml;s terminaline varacaksınız. Kendiniz terminalden otelinize veya havalimanına gidebilirsiniz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Turumuz burada sona eriyor.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">NOT:</span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Oteller oda ve kahvaltı şeklindedir. Giriş zamanı 14:00 ve &ccedil;ıkış saati 11:00&#39;dedir.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">T&uuml;m turlar sabittir. &Ouml;zel tur se&ccedil;enekleri i&ccedil;in l&uuml;tfen bizimle irtibata ge&ccedil;iniz.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Programlarımız sizin i&ccedil;in uygun değilse, program &uuml;zerinde herhangi bir değişiklik yapabilirsiniz. Seyahat planınız &uuml;zerinde birlikte &ccedil;alışabiliriz.</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">K&ouml;t&uuml; hava koşulları nedeniyle programlar değişebilir.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">İstanbul arası gidiş d&ouml;n&uuml;ş otob&uuml;s bileti</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bir gece konaklama</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">golf arabası gezi turu</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">g&uuml;nl&uuml;k şehir turu</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">kahvaltı</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&ouml;ğle yemeği</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">giriş bedeli</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">t&uuml;m yerel ulaşımlar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">profesyonel rehberler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">kişisel masraflar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">bahşişler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Otelden servis.</span></p>\n', '', '2 Günlük', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 7 g&uuml;n &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Safranbolu, geleneksel T&uuml;rk yaşamını ve k&uuml;lt&uuml;r&uuml;n&uuml; temsil eden zengin sanat eserleri koleksiyonu ile eski Osmanlı-T&uuml;rk evlerinin g&ouml;rkemli bir koleksiyonuna sahip bir kasabadır.</span></span></p>\n', '2-дневный тур по Сафранболу - Амасра из Стамбула', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">ОСНОВНЫЕ ХАРАКТЕРИСТИКИ: &bull; Сафранболу &bull; Чинчи Хамам &bull; Часовая Башня &bull; Особняк Бакизаделер &bull; Базар Араста Дом Чинджи Ходжа &bull; Амасра</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">ОТПРАВКА ИЗ СТАМБУЛА: Мы заберём вас из Султанахмета в 22:30 и отправимся к терминалу. Сядем на автобус из Стамбула в Сафранболу в 23:59. Дорога займет около 7 часов.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1-й день &ndash; ПРОГУЛКА В САФРАНБОЛУ НА МАШИНЕ ДЛЯ ГОЛЬФА</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Мы отвезём вас от автовокзала Сафранболу до города Сафранболу. Вы можете присоединиться к нашей поездке на машине для гольфа в любое время дня; Это займет около полутора часов. Мы прогуляемся по узким улочкам и остановимся в некоторых важных местах (старые деревянные дома, базары, бани, площади, мечети и т. Д.), Чтобы сфотографироваться и узнать о них побольше. Во время экскурсии мы увидим баню Чинчи Хаммам, Часовую Башню, базар Араста, особняк Бакизаделер, мост Топчу, Дом Чинджи Ходжа, бывшее правительственное здание и кузнечный рынок. У вас будет свободное время в конце дня.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Мы поселимся в историческом османском доме в Сафранболу.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">ДЕНЬ 2 &ndash; ТУР ПО АМАСРЕ (B, L)</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Мы встретимся около 10.00 в нашем офисе в Сафранболу. Сегодня мы отправимся на побережье Черного моря в Амасру. До обеда посетим музей. После обеда в рыбном ресторане мы продолжим знакомство с Римским Замком и его стенами, посетим рынок ремесленных изделий из дерева и продолжим осматривать пирс с внутренней и внешней стороны города. Около 17:00 мы вернемся в Сафранболу.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">В 23:59 вы сядете на автобус до Стамбула. Дорога занимает около 7 часов (вы не будете возвращаться в Стамбул, мы можем организовать автобус к другим городам в Турции из Сафранболу).</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">ПРИБЫТИЕ В СТАМБУЛ: Вы прибудете на автовокзал в Стамбул рано утром. Вы можете отправиться в свой отель или аэропорт из терминала самостоятельно.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Наш тур заканчивается здесь.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">ПРИМЕЧАНИЕ:</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Отель предоставит вам постель и завтрак. Время заселения 14:00, а время выселения 11:00.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Все туры являются фиксированными. Пожалуйста, свяжитесь с нами для специальных вариантов тура.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Если наши программы не подходят для вас, вы можете внести любые изменения в программу. Мы можем работать вместе над вашим планом путешествия.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Программы могут измениться из-за плохих погодных условий.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Автобус в Стамбул туда и обратно</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Одна ночь пребывания</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Обзорная экскурсия на машине для гольфа</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Дневная экскурсия по городу</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Завтрак</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Обед</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Входной билет</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Весь местный транспорт</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Профессиональные гиды</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Сервис из отеля.</span></p>\n', '', '2 дня', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">7 дней до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сафранболу - город с великолепной коллекцией старинных османско-турецких домов с богатой коллекцией произведений искусства, представляющих традиционную турецкую жизнь и культуру.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(110, '3 Days Safranbolu Amasra Tour From İstanbul', '3-Days-Safranbolu-Amasra-Tour-From-istanbul', '37431-safranbolu-cam-teras-2-1920x1080.jpg', '3e75f-safranbolu-cam-teras-2.jpg', '13120', 44, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">HIGHLIGHTS: &bull; Safranbolu &bull; Cinci Turkish Bath &bull; Clock Tower &bull; Bakizadeler Mansion &bull; Arasta Bazaar &bull; Cinci Hodja House &bull; Incekaya Aqueduct &bull; Crystal Terrace &bull; Bulak Cave &bull; Yoruk Village &bull; Amasra</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>DEPARTURE FROM ISTANBUL:</strong>&nbsp;Shuttle from Sultanahmet around 22:30 to the bus station where you will get the overnight public bus from Istanbul to Safranbolu around 23:59. The road takes about 7 hours.<br />\n	<br />\n	<strong>DAY 1 - GOLF CART SIGHTSEEING TOUR IN SAFRANBOLU</strong><br />\n	Pick up from Safranbolu bus station to old town of Safranbolu. You can join our Golf cart sightseeing tour anytime in the day; it takes about one hour and a half. We will drive through the narrow streets and stop at some important places (old wooden houses, bazaars, hamams, squares, mosque, etc) to take photos and get some information about them. We will see Cinci Turkish bath, Clock Tower, Arasta Bazaar, Bakizadeler Mansion, Topcu Bridge, Cinci Hodja House, the old government building, blacksmiths bazaar during the tour. Free time for the rest of the day.<br />\n	<br />\n	Accommodation in a historical Ottoman house in Safranbolu<br />\n	<br />\n	<strong>DAY 2 &ndash; INCEKAYA AQUEDUCT &ndash; CRYSTAL TERRACE &ndash; BULAK CAVE &ndash; YORUK VILLAGE (B, L)</strong><br />\n	Meeting at our office in Safranbolu around 11:00am. We will start visiting Incekaya Aqueduct and Crystal Terrace overlooking Tokatli Canyon which is an amazing hiking trail. Then, we will drive to Bulak Cave which is famous for its unusual geology, rare formations, and pristine condition. Our last stop will be Yoruk Village. It is an original Turkish-Ottoman village similar to an open air museum at the moment, where we can visit Sipahiler Museum and Laundry Museum. Return to Safranbolu around 15:00.<br />\n	<br />\n	Accommodation in a historical Ottoman house in Safranbolu<br />\n	<br />\n	<strong>DAY 3 -&nbsp;AMASRA TOUR&nbsp;(B, L)</strong><br />\n	Meeting at our office in Safranbolu around 10:00am. Today, we will drive toward the Black Sea coast to visit Amasra. We will visit the museum before lunch. After having lunch at a fish restaurant, we will continue our tour seeing the Roman Castle and Walls, wood-carving handicraft bazaar, and outer and inner piers of the city. Return to Safranbolu around 17:00.<br />\n	<br />\n	Overnight public bus to Istanbul around 23:59. The road takes about 7 hours (if you will not return to Istanbul, we can arrange bus from Safranbolu to any other cities in Turkey).<br />\n	<br />\n	<strong>ARRIVAL TO ISTANBUL:</strong>&nbsp;You will arrive to Istanbul main bus station early in the morning. You will have your own way to your hotel or airport.&nbsp;<br />\n	<br />\n	<strong>END OF OUR SERVICE</strong><br />\n	<br />\n	Safranbolu is in the&nbsp;UNESCO World Heritage List.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>NOTES</strong><br />\n	&bull; Please ask for a single supplement.<br />\n	&bull; Hotels are based on bed and breakfast. Check in time is 14:00 and check out time is 11:00.<br />\n	&bull; All tours are regular. Please contact us for private tour options.<br />\n	&bull; You can make any changes on the programme, if our programs are not suitable for you. We can work together on your itinerary.<br />\n	&bull; Programmes may change due to bad weather conditions.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Safranbolu</strong>&nbsp;is a town boasting a glorious collection of old Ottoman-Turkish houses, with a rich collection of art masterpieces which represent the traditional Turkish life and culture.<br />\n	<strong>Yoruk Village</strong>&nbsp;is close to Safranbolu. It looks like a small Safranbolu, but more authentic and untouched. People in the village are living as they did in the past.<br />\n	<strong>Incekaya Aqueduct</strong>&nbsp;was built by Izzet Mahmet Pasha to provide water from the source to the town of Safranbolu. It is a magnificent structure with 6 arches on the bridge.<br />\n	<strong>Crystal Terrace</strong>&nbsp;was built by steel and resistant glass with a bearing capacity of 70.000kg overlooking Tokatli Canyon which is an amazing hiking trail.<br />\n	<strong>Bulak Cave&nbsp;</strong>is the fourth longest explored cave in Turkey with 6.042m in length. It is famous for its unusual geology, rare formations, and pristine condition. About 450meters can be visited.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 43, 73);\">INCLUDED</span></strong></span></span><span mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" new=\"\" segoe=\"\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\" times=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: -18pt; line-height: normal;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 43, 73);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 43, 73);\">Round trip overnight public bus tickets from/to Istanbul</span></span></span><span new=\"\" segoe=\"\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;\nfont-family:\" times=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n	<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: -18pt; line-height: normal;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 43, 73);\">&nbsp;2</span>