style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Тур по Сафранболу на весь день</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Места для посещения:</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Холм Хыдырлык, музей губернаторов округа, медные мастерские, сапожники и базар Эйджилер, мечеть Иззет Мехмет-Паша, Чинчи Хан, Базар Араста, мечеть Кёпрюлю, солнечные часы, хаммам Чинчи, старое государственное здание и часовая башня.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Озеро Дипсиз, деревня Йорук (перерыв на чай), дом-музей Сипахилера, музей белья и цветок шафран, холм Хидирлик</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Профессиональный гид</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Все входные билеты</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Весь транспорт</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Обед</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сервис из отеля.</span></span></p>\n', '', '8-9 часов', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(112, 'Fethiye Dalyan Mud Bath ', 'Fethiye-Dalyan-Mud-Bath-', '1e6fa-amur-banyosu4.jpg', 'bac66-amur-banyosu4.jpg', '6115', 37, '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">The daily Dalyan mud bath journey starts with a coach transfer from your resort to Dalyan village which is 30 km away from Dalaman Airport and 65 km from Fethiye. Dalyan is a small county of Mugla city located between the Marmaris and Fethiye districts.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Pick Up: Calis 09:00 Fethiye 08:30 Oludeniz 08:00 Hisaronu 08:30</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Drop Off: Approximately 18:30</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.95pt;margin-left:\n0cm\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">The daily Dalyan mud bath journey starts with a coach transfer from your resort to Dalyan village which is 30 km away from Dalaman Airport and 65 km from Fethiye. Dalyan is a small county of Mugla city located between the Marmaris and Fethiye districts.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.95pt;margin-left:\n0cm\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Our agenda of&nbsp;<strong>Dalyan Mud Bath</strong>&nbsp;day will start with Dalyan river boat trip. This romantic tour on the Dalyan river estuary will take us to another interesting point where we will refresh our skin with sulphuric mud baths. But on the way to Dalyan Mud Bath, we will enjoy the scenery of the reeds and nature and also the famous rock tombs of Dalyan. After this amazing Dalyan river boat trip we will reach to famous Dalyan Mud Bath. It&#39;s believed that the mud baths makes you feel and look younger and a dip in the sulphur springs after the mud bath will freshen you.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">One thing we are sure about the Dalyan Mud Bath is that you will feel hungry after it. We will serve an open buffet lunch in the village after the Mud Bath adventure. Different selections of traditional Turkish food is waiting for your taste.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Next item on the agenda will be a relaxing swim stop at Iztuzu beach. You can choose either the freshwater or saltwater, the turquoise waters of Mediterranean sea to swim. If you are lucky you may see some Caretta Caretta turtles on the beach.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">After the swim break at the Iztuzu beach we will return to our coach with the last part of the boat trip and head back to Fethiye. On the boat you may have a chance to taste the blue crab!</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<u><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Available Days: Mon, Wed, Sat</span></span></u></p>\n', '<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">INCLUDED</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Transport</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Insurance</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Lunch</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Boat Trip</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Mud Bath Fee</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">EXCULED:</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Drinks</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick Up: Calis 09:00 Fethiye 08:30 Oludeniz 08:00 Hisaronu 08:30</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bring Along: Swimsuit, Sun cream, Towel, Camera</span></span></span></p>\n', '9-10 Hours', 0, '1', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">English, Russian speaking tour guide.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The daily Dalyan mud bath journey starts with a coach transfer from your resort to Dalyan village which is 30 km away from Dalaman Airport and 65 km from Fethiye. Dalyan is a small county of Mugla city located between the Marmaris and Fethiye districts.</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 0, 75, 'Dalyan Çamur Banyosu', '<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.95pt;margin-left:\n0cm\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Dalyan &ccedil;amur banyosu turu, otelinizden sizi alacak tur otob&uuml;s&uuml;m&uuml;zle yapacağınız yolculuk ile başlar. Dalyan, Dalaman havaalanına 30 km, Fethiye&rsquo;ye ise ortalama 65 km mesafededir. Dalyan, Marmaris ve Fethiye il&ccedil;eleri arasında yer alan Muğla&#39;nın k&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;k bir il&ccedil;esidir.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.95pt;margin-left:\n0cm\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Alış Saati: &Ccedil;alış 09:00 Fethiye 08:30 &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz 08:00 Hisar&ouml;n&uuml; 08:30</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Bırakış Saati: Tahmini 18:30</strong></span></span></p>\n', '<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.95pt;margin-left:\n0cm\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Dalyan &ccedil;amur banyosu turu, otelinizden sizi alacak tur otob&uuml;s&uuml;m&uuml;zle yapacağınız yolculuk ile başlar. Dalyan, Dalaman havaalanına 30 km, Fethiye&rsquo;ye ise ortalama 65 km mesafededir. Dalyan, Marmaris ve Fethiye il&ccedil;eleri arasında yer alan Muğla&#39;nın k&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;k bir il&ccedil;esidir.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Dalyan &Ccedil;amur Banyosu</strong>&nbsp;tur programımız Dalyan nehrinde yapılacak bir tekne turu ile devam eder. Dalyan nehrinde yapılan bu romantik tekne turu sizi, cildinizi s&uuml;lf&uuml;rik &ccedil;amur banyolarıyla yenileyeceğiniz başka ilgin&ccedil; bir noktaya g&ouml;t&uuml;recektir. Ancak Dalyan &Ccedil;amur Banyosu yolunda sazların ve doğa manzarasının, ayrıca Dalyan&#39;ın meşhur kaya mezarlarının da tadını &ccedil;ıkaracaksınız. Bu şaşırtıcı Dalyan nehri tekne turundan sonra &uuml;nl&uuml; Dalyan &Ccedil;amur Banyosu&#39;na ulaşacağız. &Ccedil;amur banyolarının kendinizi daha gen&ccedil; hissetmenizi ve daha gen&ccedil; g&ouml;r&uuml;nmenizi sağladığına inanılmaktadır. &Ccedil;amur banyosundan hemen sonra sizi tazeleleyecek k&uuml;k&uuml;rt kaynaklarına girerek cildinizi temizleyip rahatlayabilirsiniz.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Dalyan &Ccedil;amur Banyosu&#39;ndan emin olduğumuz şeylerden biri, hemen sonra kendinizi a&ccedil; hissedeceğiniz olmasıdır. &Ccedil;amur Banyosu macerasından sonra k&ouml;yde a&ccedil;ık b&uuml;fe &ouml;ğle yemeği servis edeceğiz. Geleneksel T&uuml;rk yemeklerinden farklı se&ccedil;imler sizi bekliyor olacak.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ajandamızdaki bir sonraki durak İztuzu plajında rahatlatıcı bir y&uuml;zme molası olacak. Tatlı su veya tuzlu su, y&uuml;zmek i&ccedil;in Akdeniz&#39;in turkuaz suları arasından se&ccedil;im yapabilirsiniz. Şanslıysanız sahilde bazı Caretta Caretta kaplumbağaları g&ouml;rebilirsiniz.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">İztuzu plajında y&uuml;zme molasından sonra tekne turunun son b&ouml;l&uuml;m&uuml; ile otob&uuml;s&uuml;m&uuml;ze geri d&ouml;neceğiz ve Fethiye&#39;ye yola &ccedil;ıkacağız. Eğer ilginizi &ccedil;ekerse teknede mavi yenge&ccedil;leri tadma şansınız olabilir!</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><u><strong>Başlangı&ccedil; Tarihi: 1 May 2018</strong></u></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><u><strong>Yaş Limiti: 0+</strong></u></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><u><strong>M&uuml;sait G&uuml;nler: Pzt, &Ccedil;rş, Cts</strong></u></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Transfer</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sigorta</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ouml;ğlen Yemeği</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Tekne Turu</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ccedil;amur Banyosu Girişi</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">İ&ccedil;ecekler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Alış Saati: &Ccedil;alış 09:00 Fethiye 08:30 &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz 08:00 Hisar&ouml;n&uuml; 08:30</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Yanınızda Getirin: Deniz Kıyafeti, G&uuml;neş Kremi, Kamera, Havlu</span></span></p>\n', '9-10 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan rehber</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Turdan 24 Saat &ouml;nce.</span></span></p>\n', '', 'Грязевые ванны Дальян', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Экскурсия грязевых ванн Дальян начинается на автобусе, который отвезёт вас туда из отеля. Дальян находится в 30 км от аэропорта Даламан и в 65 км от Фетхие. Дальян - это небольшой городок в области Мугла между Мармарисом и Фетхие Мугла.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Время отправления: 09:00 Фетхие 08:30 Мёртвое море 08:00 Хисарёню 08:30</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong>Время прибытия: Приблизительно 18:30</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Экскурсия грязевых ванн Дальян начинается в автобуеа, который отвезёт вас туда из отеля. Дальян находится в 30 км от аэропорта Даламан и в 65 км от Фетхие. Дальян - это небольшой городок в области Мугла между Мармарисом и Фетхие Мугла.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Программа грязевых ванн Дальян продолжается экскурсией на лодке по реке Дальян. Этот романтический тур на лодке по реке Дальян перенесет вас в другое интересное место, где вы сможете с помощью серно-грязевых ванн освежить свою кожу. А также вы сможете насладиться тростником и природными пейзажами в грязевых ваннах Дальян и знаменитых скальных гробницах Дальян. После этой удивительной прогулки на лодке по реке Далянь мы достигнем знаменитых грязевых ванн Далян. Считается, что грязевые ванны дают ощущение молодости. Сразу после грязевой ванны с источниками серы вы сможете расслабиться, отдохнуть и освежиться.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">После грязевых ванн Дальян вы вскоре почувствуете голод. После приключений с грязевыми ваннами, мы педоставим &laquo;шведский стол&raquo; на обед в деревне. Вас ждут различные блюда традиционной турецкой кухни.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Следующая остановка на повестке дня - расслабляющий отдых на пляже Изтузу.&nbsp; Для купания вы можете выбрать пресную или солёную воды или же бирюзовые&nbsp; воды Средиземного моря. Если вам повезёт, вы можете увидеть морских черепах породы каретта-каретта на пляже.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">После плавательного перерыва на пляже Изтузу мы вернёмся к автобусу&nbsp; для того чтобы отправиться на последнюю&nbsp; часть нашей экскурсии на лодке и отправимся в Фетхие. Если вам интересно, у вас может быть шанс попробовать на&nbsp; вкус &laquo;синего краба&raquo; на лодке!</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<strong style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><u>Возрастное ограничение: 0+</u></strong></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Доступные дни: пн, ср, сб</u></strong></span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Трансфер</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Страхование</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Обед</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Тур на лодке</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Вход в грязевую ванну</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Напитки</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Время отправления: 09:00 Фетхие 08:30 Мёртвое море 08:00 Хисарёню 08:30</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Возьмите с собой: одежда для плаванья, солнцезащитный крем, фотоаппарат, полотенце</span></span></p>\n', '9-10часов', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(113, 'Fethiye Oludeniz Boat Trips', 'Fethiye-Oludeniz-Boat-Trips', '4bccc-fethiye-boat-tour.jpg', '06a47-fethiye-boat-tour.jpg', '6120', 37, '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">If you are looking for different bays and beaches for a day out on boat, Oludeniz Boat Trip is the right trip for you. Jump on board and enjoy the sun shine and wind.</span></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick Up: Calis 09:15 Fethiye 09:45 Oludeniz 10:00 Hisaronu 09:45</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Drop Off: Approximately 18:00</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Get ready to be collected from your resort / hotel in the morning. We advise you to have your breakfast before pick up time. We will drive you to Oludeniz aka. Blue Lagoon (rated among the top 5 most beautiful beaches of the world, 15 km from Fethiye centre), to your traditional wooden Turkish Gulet. When all the customers arrive, we will start our tour of &ldquo;Oludeniz Boat Trip&rdquo;.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">There will be 5 or 6 stops during the day and some of these places are only reachable by boat. It&#39;s a natural cave with turquoise crystal waters. Next stop will be a visit to the famous Butterfly Valley. You may leave the boat and do a short hiking in the valley and visit the waterfall of the valley. If you are lucky, you can see some of the butterflies. There are hundreds of different types of butterflies in this amazing valley. If you prefer to swim, sandy beach of Butterfly Valley is waiting for you.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Later, our captain will take us the the historical church and the ruins of St. Nicholas Island. This island is known as the house of St. Nicholas or as everybody knows, &ldquo;Santa Claus&rdquo;. A perfect water will invite you for snorkeling here. There is a fresh water source leaking into sea around the island so you may find the water a bit refreshing in some spots.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">On the way back to Oludeniz we will see and visit different bays and places. There will be lunch served on the boat, (barbecue) fish or chicken, pasta or rice, salad, mezzes and fresh fruits. We are sure that you&rsquo;ll never forget this relaxing tour of Oludeniz Boat Trips.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Available Days: Thu, Sun</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">INCLUDED</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Transport</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Insurance</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Lunch</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Boat Trip</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">EXCULED:</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Drinks</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Pick Up: Calis 09:15 Fethiye 09:45 Oludeniz 10:00 Hisaronu 09:45</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Bring Along: Swimsuit, Sun cream, Towel, Camera</span></p>\n', '8-9 Hours', 0, '', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">English speaking tour guide.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">If you are looking for different bays and beaches for a day out on boat, Oludeniz Boat Trip is the right trip for you. Jump on board and enjoy the sun shine and wind.</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 0, 76, 'Ölüdeniz Bot Turu', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Farklı koylar ve plajlarda gezeceğiniz, daha &ouml;nce g&ouml;rmediğiniz yerler g&ouml;receğiniz bir tekne turu arıyorsanız &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz Tekne Turu sizin i&ccedil;in doğru tur olacaktır. Ahşap guletlerimize atlayıp g&uuml;neşin ve denizin keyfini &ccedil;ıkarın.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Alış Saati: &Ccedil;alış 09:15 Fethiye 09:45 &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz 10:00 Hisar&ouml;n&uuml; 09:45</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bırakış Saati: Tahmini 18:00</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Farklı koylar ve plajlarda gezeceğiniz, daha &ouml;nce g&ouml;rmediğiniz yerler g&ouml;receğiniz bir tekne turu arıyorsanız &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz Tekne Turu sizin i&ccedil;in doğru tur olacaktır. Ahşap guletlerimize atlayıp g&uuml;neşin ve denizin keyfini &ccedil;ıkarın.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Sabah aracımız sizi otel/evinizden alacak ve teknemize getirecektir. Gelmeden &ouml;nce kahvaltı yapmanızı &ouml;neriyoruz. Aracımız sizi Blue Lagoon olarak bilinen (d&uuml;nyanın en g&uuml;zel 5 plajı arasında, Fethiye merkezine 15 km uzaklıkta) &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz&#39;e getirecek ve burada geleneksel ahşap T&uuml;rk guletimize bineceksiniz. T&uuml;m m&uuml;şterilerimizin teknemize binmesinin ardından &ldquo;&Ouml;l&uuml;deniz Tekne Turu&rdquo; muz başlayacak.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">G&uuml;n boyunca 5 veya 6 noktada duracağız ve bu yerlerin bazılarına yalnızca tekne ile ulaşılabiliyor. Duraklarımızdan biri d&uuml;nyaca &uuml;nl&uuml; Kelebekler Vadisi yolu &uuml;zerindeki Mavi Mağara olacak. Mavi Mağara y&uuml;zmek ve şnorkel ile su altını incelemek i&ccedil;in muhteşem bir noktadır. Mavi mağara turkuaz kristal suları olan doğal bir mağaradır. Bir sonraki durağımız &uuml;nl&uuml; Kelebekler Vadisi. Tekneden ayrılıp vadide kısa bir y&uuml;r&uuml;y&uuml;ş yapabilir ve şelaleyi ziyaret edebilirsiniz. Burada aynı zamanda y&uuml;zme molası da vereceğiz. Eğer şanslı g&uuml;n&uuml;n&uuml;zde iseniz vadiye adını veren kelebekleri g&ouml;rebilirsiniz. Bu şaşırtıcı vadide y&uuml;zlerce farklı kelebek t&uuml;r&uuml; vardır. Y&uuml;zmeyi tercih ederseniz, Kelebekler Vadisi&#39;nin kumlu plajı sizi bekliyor.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Daha sonra kaptanımız, tarihi kilise ve kalıntıları olan St. Nicholas Adası&#39;na doğru yola &ccedil;ıkacaktır. Bu ada St. Nicholas&#39;ın ya da herkesin bildiği gibi &quot;Noel Baba&quot; nın evi olarak olarak bilinir. Burada m&uuml;kemmel bir su sizi şnorkelle dolaşmaya davet edecek. Adanın etrafından &ccedil;ıkan taze su kaynakları vardır, bu nedenle suyun biraz noktalarında ferahlatıcı olduğunu hissedebilirsiniz.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&Ouml;l&uuml;deniz&#39;e d&ouml;nerken farklı koyları ve &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz&#39;in muhteşem manzarasını g&ouml;receğiz. Teknede balık veya tavuk, makarna veya pilav, salata, mezeler ve taze meyveler i&ccedil;eren &ouml;ğle yemeği sunulacaktır. Bu muhteşem &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz Tekne Turu&rsquo;nu unutamayacağınıza eminiz.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<font face=\"raleway, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Tekne Turu</span></font></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Sigorta</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">a&ccedil;ık b&uuml;fe &ouml;ğle yemeği</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<font face=\"raleway, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">İ&ccedil;ecekler</span></font></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">kişisel masraflar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">bahşişler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Transfer Yerleri: Fethiye, &Ccedil;alış, &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz, Hisar&ouml;n&uuml;</span></span></p>\n', '', '8-9 Saat', '<p>\n	Rehbersiz</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Turdan 24 saat &ouml;nce</span></span></p>\n', '', 'Экскурсия по Мёртвому морю на лодке ', '<p>\n	Экскурсия по Мёртвому морю на лодке подойдет вам, если вы ищете лодочный тур и увидите то, что нигде раньше не видели в разных заливах и на пляжах. Прыгайте в наши деревянные бригантины, наслаждайтесь солнцем и морем.</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Время отправления: работает 09:15 Фетхие 09:45 Мёртвое море 10:00 Хисарону 09:45</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Время прибытия: приблизительно18:00</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Экскурсия по Мёртвому морю на лодке подойдёт вам, если вы ищете лодочный тур и увидите то, что нигде раньше не видели в разных заливах и на пляжах. Прыгайте в наши деревянные бригантины, наслаждайтесь солнцем и морем.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Утром наш автомобиль заберёт вас из отеля / дома и привезёт к лодке. Мы рекомендуем вам не завтракать до приезда. Наш автомобиль доставит вас к Мёртвому морю, известное как Голубая Лагуна (15 км от центра Фетхие, между 5 самыми красивыми пляжами в мире). После того, как все наши клиенты сядут на нашу лодку, на Мёртвом море начнется тур &laquo;банан&raquo;.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">На протяжении дня мы остановимся в 5 или 6 точках, и до некоторых из этих мест можно добраться только на лодке. Одна из наших остановок - Голубая Пещера по всемирно известной дороге Долины Бабочек. Голубая пещера - сказочное место для плавания и изучения подводного плавания с трубкой. Голубая пещера - это природная пещера с бирюзовой кристально чистой водой. Наша следующая остановка - знаменитая Долина Бабочек. Вы можете покинуть лодку и совершить небольшую прогулку по долине и посетить водопад. Мы также сделаем здесь перерыв для того чтобы вы могли поплавать. Если вам повезёт, вы сможете увидеть бабочек, которые и дали такое название долине. В этой удивительной долине есть сотни различных видов бабочек. Если вы захотите поплавать, вас ждет песчаный пляж Долины Бабочек.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Затем наш капитан поедет прямо к исторической церкви и руинам Острова св. Николая. Это остров св. Николая известен как дом &laquo;Санта Клауса&raquo;(&laquo;Деда Мороза&raquo;). Вы можете заняться снорклингом и погрузиться в превосходный водный мир. Вокруг этого острова есть источники пресной воды, поэтому вам может показаться, что вода немного освежает.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">На обратном пути к Мёртвому морю мы увидим различные бухты и его великолепные виды. Вам будет подан обед на лодке с рыбой или курицей, пастой или рисом, салатами, закусками и свежими фруктами. Мы уверены, что вы никогда не забудете этот великолепный тур на лодке по Мёртвому морю.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Тур на лодке</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Страховка</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Обед &laquo;шведский стол&raquo;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Напитки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Места трансфера: Фетхие, Калис, Мёртвое море, Хисарёню</span></span></p>\n', '', '8-9 часов', '<p>\n	-</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
