(114, 'Fethiye Saklıkent Tlos Yakapark Tour', 'Fethiye-Saklikent-Tlos-Yakapark-Tour', '589f9-saklikent-tlos-yakapark.jpg', '25014-saklikent-tlos-yakapark.jpg', '6125', 37, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">This is a daily tour to Saklikent Gorge, Tlos ancient city and Yakapark nature park from Fethiye.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick Up: Calis 09:00 Fethiye 08:30 Oludeniz 08:00 Hisaronu 08:30</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Drop Off: Approximately 18:30</span></span></p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Tour starts with the pick up from your resort / hotel and drive to mountain road of Antalya, to Saklikent Gorge which is 50 km away from Fethiye.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">During the day, we will visit the ruins of Tlos city which was an Lycian city and the settlement here is 4000 years old. The city is ruined but historian and archaeologist says that the city was one of the most important religious city of Lycia. The settlement of the city is on the hills and its believed in the mythology that Bellerophon lived in Tlos with his flying horse Pegasus and he has a king type tomb in the necropolis dedicated by citizens of Lycia.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">After the mystic air of Tlos, we will go to a trout farm in Yaka village, a hand made heaven with full of water gardens and traditional restaurants. Lunch of fresh trout (or chicken) and a large selection of salads and mezzes will be waiting us here.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">And the famous gorge! Saklikent! Saklikent gorge is the second longest gorge in Europe. We have to warn you before you get into the water! Its icy cold! You can jump into the water and explore the canyon by yourself or a private guide or if its too cold for you just relax and enjoy the moment on the riverside cafes with a nice hot tea or coffee. Ok! A cold beer will be good too!</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">After the long day, our coach will drive us back to Fethiye.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">INCLUDED</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Transport</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Insurance</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Lunch</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Boat Trip</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">EXCULED:</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Drinks</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick Up: Calis 09:00 Fethiye 08:30 Oludeniz 08:00 Hisaronu 08:30</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Bring Along: Swimsuit, Sun cream, Towel, Camera</span></p>\n', '9-10 Hours', 0, '1', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">English speaking tour guide.</span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This is a daily tour to Saklikent Gorge, Tlos ancient city and Yakapark nature park from Fethiye.&nbsp;</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 0, 77, 'Saklıkent Tlos Yakapark Turu', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bu tur Fethiye kalkışlı olup Saklıkent vadisi ve Tlos antik kenti ile Yakapark Doğa Parkı gezilerini kapsayan bir g&uuml;nl&uuml;k turdur. Tura, sizi otelinizden aldıktan sonra Antalya&#39;nın dağ yolundan Fethiye&#39;ye 50 km uzaklıktaki Saklıkent Vadisi y&ouml;n&uuml;ne gidişle başlayacağız.</span></span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Alış Saati: &Ccedil;alış 09:00 Fethiye 08:30 &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz 08:00 Hisar&ouml;n&uuml; 08:30</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bırakış Saati: Tahmini 18:30</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bu tur Fethiye kalkışlı olup Saklıkent vadisi ve Tlos antik kenti ile Yakapark Doğa Parkı gezilerini kapsayan bir g&uuml;nl&uuml;k turdur. Tura, sizi otelinizden aldıktan sonra Antalya&#39;nın dağ yolundan Fethiye&#39;ye 50 km uzaklıktaki Saklıkent Vadisi y&ouml;n&uuml;ne gidişle başlayacağız.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Yol &uuml;zerinde yerleşimi yaklaşık 4000 yıl &ouml;ncesine giden bir Likya kenti Tlos&#39;un kalıntılarını ziyaret edeceğiz. Yıkık durumda olan Tlos kenti i&ccedil;in tarih&ccedil;i ve arkeologlar Likya&#39;nın en &ouml;nemli dini kentlerinden biri olduğunu s&ouml;ylemektedir. Kentin yerleşimi tepelerdedir ve mitolojide kral Bellerophon&#39;un U&ccedil;an Atı Pegasus ile Tlos&#39;da yaşadığına inanılır. Bellerophon&#39;un kral mezarı Likya vatandaşlarına tahsis edilen mezarlıkta bulunmaktadır.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Tlos&#39;un mistik havasından sonra, havuzlu bah&ccedil;eler ve geleneksel restoranlar ile dolu el yapımı cennet olan Yaka k&ouml;y&uuml;ndeki bir alabalık &ccedil;iftliğine gideceğiz. Taze alabalıklı (veya tavuklu) &ouml;ğle yemeği ile geniş bir salata ve meze men&uuml;s&uuml; burada bizi bekliyor olacak.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Ve &uuml;nl&uuml; vadi! Saklıkent! Saklıkent vadisi, Avrupa&#39;daki ikinci en uzun boğazdır. Suya girmeden &ouml;nce sizi uyarmak zorundayız, kanyonun doğal kaynak suyu 0 dereceye yakın bir soğukluktadır. Suya atlayabilir, kanyonu kendiniz veya &ouml;zel bir rehberle keşfedebilirsiniz. Su sizin i&ccedil;in &ccedil;ok soğuksa nehir kenarındaki kafelerde &ccedil;ay / kahve i&ccedil;erekte rahatlayıp keyifli vakit ge&ccedil;irebilirsiniz. Tabi soğuk bir bira da &ccedil;ok iyi olabilir!</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Uzun g&uuml;n&uuml;n ardından kaptanımız bizi Fethiye&#39;ye geri g&ouml;t&uuml;recektir.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Profesyonel rehber</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">t&uuml;m giriş &uuml;cretleri</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">t&uuml;m ulaşımlar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">a&ccedil;ık b&uuml;fe &ouml;ğle yemeği</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<font face=\"raleway, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">İ&ccedil;ecekler</span></font></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">kişisel masraflar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">bahşişler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Otelden servis.</span></span></p>\n', '', '9-10 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '', 'Тур по Саклыкент Тлос Якапарк ', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Это однодневный тур по Фетхие, который включает в себя Ущелье Саклыкент и древний город Тлос и природный парк Якапарк. После того как вас заберут из отеля, мы отправися в Саклыкент по горной дороге Анталии,что в 50 км от долины Фетхие.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Время отправления: Калис 09:00 Фетхие 08:30 Мёртвое море 08:00 Хисарёню 08:30</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Время прибытия: приблизительно 18:30</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Это однодневный тур по Фетхие, который включает в себя Ущелье Саклыкент и древний город Тлос и природный парк Якапарк. После того как вас заберут из отеля, мы отправимся в Саклыкент по горной дороге Анталии, что в 50 км от долины Фетхие.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; По дороге мы посетим руины ликийского города Тлос, который был заселён около 4000 лет назад. Историки и археологи говорят, что город Тлос это один из самых важных религиозных городов Ликии. Посёлок города находится на холмах, и в мифологии считается, что король Беллерофон жил в Тлосе с Летающим Конем Пегасом. Царская гробница Беллерофона находится на кладбище, которое отведено жителям Ликии.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; После мистической атмосферы Тлоса мы отправимся на форелевое хозяйство в деревне Яка, как будто построенный руками рай, полный садов у бассейна и традиционных ресторанов. Здесь нас ждёт обед из свежей форели (или курицы) с обширным меню салатов и закусок.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; И знаменитая долина! Саклыкент! Ущелье Саклыкент, это ущелье является вторым по длине проливом в Европе. Мы должны предупредить вас, что температура природной родниковой воды каньона приблизительно 0 градусов. Вы можете зайти в воду, осмотреть каньон самостоятельно или с частным гидом. Если вода слишком холодная для вас, вы можете расслабиться и выпить чай / кофе в прибрежных кафе. Конечно же холодное пиво тоже будет кстати!</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; После долгого дня наш капитан отвезет нас в Фетхие.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Профессиональный гид</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Все входные билеты</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Весь транспорт</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; &laquo;Шведский стол&raquo;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Напитки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сервис из отеля.</span></span></p>\n', '', '9-10 часов', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(115, '12 Islands Daily Boat Tour', '12-Islands-Daily-Boat-Tour', '7bbc8-12-islands-daily-boat-tour.jpg', '9d191-12-islands-daily-boat-tour.jpg', '6130', 37, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">The best activity on a holiday is to take a boat and cruise through different spots and islands of the area so 12 İslands boat tour is the best choice for you.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick Up: Calis 09:30 Fethiye 09:45 Oludeniz 09:00 Hisaronu 09:30</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Drop Off: Approximately 18:00</span></span></p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Turkey has lots of beauty and treasures but there are more to be discovered and seen only by the sea. We have beautiful beaches, clear turquoise waters and every single spot of the coast line is full of history!</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">One of the best daily boat tour in Fethiye is the 12 Islands Daily Boat Tour. Your day will start with pick-up from your resort and a short drive to Fethiye harbour. As soon as all the customers welcome on board, our well trained, smiley faced staff will get ready to leave the harbour with your comfortable sail motor boat which is a traditional wooden gullet boat with engine and mast to sail.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">There will be different islands on the trip and our captain will stop on a few of them for swim and lunch break. Some of the islands can be seen only from boat. But we stop in the best of them!</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">If you want to relax and unwind this is the best choice for you. Lay down on the deck under the Mediterranean sun, listen to the whistle of the wind and have a fresh cooked meal on the deck. And a surprise! You may see some special spots that Cleopatra had visited before you!</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">INCLUDED</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Transport</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Insurance</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Lunch</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Boat Trip</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">EXCULED:</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Drinks</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Pick Up: Calis 09:30 Fethiye 09:45 Oludeniz 09:00 Hisaronu 09:30</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Bring Along: Swimsuit, Sun cream, Towel, Camera,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Snorkel</span></span></p>\n', '8-9 Hours', 0, '1', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">English speaking tour guide.</span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The best activity on a holiday is to take a boat and cruise through different spots and islands of the area so 12 İslands boat tour is the best choice for you.&nbsp;</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 0, 78, '12 Adalar Günlük Tekne Turu', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bir tatilde yapılabilecek en g&uuml;zel g&uuml;nl&uuml;k aktivite eğer Akdeniz&#39;deyseniz, bir tekneye binmek ve b&ouml;lgenin farklı noktalarını ve adalarını gezmektir. T&uuml;rkiye&#39;nin g&uuml;zellikleri ve hazineleri &ccedil;oktur, ancak keşfedilecek daha &ccedil;ok şey var ve bunların &ccedil;oğu sadece denizden g&ouml;r&uuml;lebilir. G&uuml;zel kumsallarımız, berrak turkuaz sularımız ve her bir noktası tarih dolu sahil şeridimiz...</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Alış Saati: &Ccedil;alış 09:30 Fethiye 09:45 &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz 09:00 Hisar&ouml;n&uuml; 09:30</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bırakış Saati: Tahmini 18:00</span></span></p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Fethiye&#39;de yapılan en iyi g&uuml;nl&uuml;k tekne turu 12 Adalar Tekne Turu&#39;dur. Tur sabahı servis ara&ccedil;larımız sizleri otellerinizden alıp Fethiye limanına getirir. T&uuml;m m&uuml;şteriler teknemize geldikten sonra iyi eğitilmiş, g&uuml;ler y&uuml;zl&uuml; personelimiz, motoru olan ve yelkenli direklere sahip geleneksel ahşap guletimiz ile limandan &ccedil;ıkmak i&ccedil;in hazırıklarını tamamlar ve turumuz başlar.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">G&uuml;n boyu farklı bir &ccedil;ok ada ziyaret edeceğiz, kaptanımız y&uuml;zme molası ve &ouml;ğle yemeği i&ccedil;in bu adaların en g&uuml;zellerinde duracak. Bazı adalar sadece tekneden g&ouml;r&uuml;lebilir ve yanaşmak imkansızdır ama kaptanınız en iyilerinde duracaktır!</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Dinlenmek ve rahatlamak istiyorsanız bu sizin i&ccedil;in en iyi tur se&ccedil;imi olacaktır. Akdeniz g&uuml;neşinin altında g&uuml;vertede yatın, r&uuml;zg&acirc;rın &ccedil;ıkardığı melodileri dinleyin ve g&uuml;vertede taze pişmiş yemeklerin tadını &ccedil;ıkarın. Ve bir s&uuml;rprizimiz var! Kleopatra&#39;nın sizden &ouml;nce ziyaret ettiği bazı &ouml;zel noktaları da bu turumuzda g&ouml;rebilirsiniz!</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Tekne Turu</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Sigorta</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">t&uuml;m ulaşımlar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">a&ccedil;ık b&uuml;fe &ouml;ğle yemeği</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">İ&ccedil;ecek</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">kişisel masraflar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">bahşişler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Otelden servis.</span></p>\n', '', '8-9 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '', 'Дневной тур на лодке по 12 островам ', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Самое прекрасное занятие во время отпуска днём - это если вы на Средиземном море садитесь на лодку и посещаете различные места и острова этого региона. В Турции есть много красот и сокровищ, но есть ещё больше и их можно обнаружить только с моря. Наши прекрасные песчаные пляжи, кристально чистые бирюзовые воды и каждая точка заполненная историей береговая линия ...</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Время отправления: Калыш 09:30 Фетхие 09:45 Мёртвое море 09:00 Хисарёню 09:30</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Время прибытия: приблизительно 18:00</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Это лучшая ежедневная прогулка на лодке в Фетхие - это тур на лодке по 12-му острову. Утром мы заберём вас из отлея и отвезём в порт Фетхие. После того, как все пассажиры сядут в лодку, мы начнём тур подняв паруса и покинем порт на нашей традиционной деревянной галете.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Мы посетим много разных островов в течение всего дня, наш капитан остановится на самом красивом из этих островов на плавательный перерыв и обед. Некоторые острова можно увидеть только с лодки, к ним невозможно подплыть, но ваш капитан остановится в самом лучшем месте!</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Если вы желаете расслабиться и отдохнуть, то это будет наилучшим лучшим выбором для вас. Вы лежите на палубе под средиземноморским солнцем, слушайте шум ветра и наслаждаетесь свежеприготовленными блюдами на палубе. А также у нас есть сюрприз! В этом туре вы также сможете увидеть некоторые особенные места, которые посетила Клеопатра!</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Тур на лодке</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Страховка</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Весь транспрот</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; &laquo;Шведский стол&raquo;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Напитки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сервис из отеля.</span></span></p>\n', '', '8-9 часов', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
