;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Еда и напитки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сервис из отеля.</span></span></p>\n', '', '2 часа', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(125, 'White Water Rafting Fethiye', 'White-Water-Rafting-Fethiye', '23f30-rafting-fethiye.jpeg', '41e9e-rafting-fethiye.jpg', '6180', 37, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Rafting on Dalaman River is one of the most booked daily excursion in Fethiye area.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick Up: Calis 08:15 Fethiye 08:00 Oludeniz 07:10 Hisaronu 07:25</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Drop Off: Approximately 18:30</span></span></p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">The river has 3 to 4 rapid level. Rafting is an outdoor adventure sport and here in Dalaman river you will have a chance to turn this adventure sport into a great fun day out with our experienced and qualified guides and staff. They will help and guide you downstream on the boat and they will guarantee that you will get wet and have a wild adventure.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Tour will have two parts. After education and briefing you will do the first part of the rafting. After the lunch second part will start. There will be a group of people on each boat and a professional guide. You will row down the stream and sometimes let the flowing water take guide you on the river. After the tour you can buy photos and videos of the tour.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Age Limit: 12+</span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">INCLUDED</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Transport</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Insurance</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Lunch</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Equipment</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">EXCULED:</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Drinks</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Pick Up: Calis 08:15 Fethiye 08:00 Oludeniz 07:10 Hisaronu 07:25</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bring Along: Swimsuit, Sun cream, Towel, Camera</span></span></p>\n', '9-10 Hours', 0, '1', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">English speaking tour guide.</span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Rafting on Dalaman River is one of the most booked daily excursion in Fethiye area.&nbsp;</span></p>\n', 1, 0, '18+', '12-17', '', 0, 88, 'Beyaz Su Raftingi ', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Dalaman Nehri&rsquo;nde rafting Fethiye b&ouml;lgesinin en &ccedil;ok tercih edilen g&uuml;nl&uuml;k gezi programlarından biridir.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Alış Saati: &Ccedil;alış 08:15 Fethiye 08:00 &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz 07:10 Hisar&ouml;n&uuml; 07:25</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bırakış Saati: Tahmini 18:30</span></span></p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Nehrin hız seviyesi 3-4 civarıdır. Rafting a&ccedil;ık havada ge&ccedil;en bir macera sporudur. Dalaman Nehri&rsquo;nde bu sporu deneyimli ve nitelikli rehberlerimiz ve personelimiz ile birlikte tam bir eğlence haline getireceğiz. Bot &uuml;zerinde rehberlimiz size yardımcı olacaklar. Bununla birlikte ıslancağınızı ve &ccedil;ok eğleneceğinizi garanti ederiz.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Tur iki b&ouml;l&uuml;mden oluşacak. Eğitim ve brifingden sonra raftingin ilk b&ouml;l&uuml;m&uuml;n&uuml; yapacağız. &Ouml;ğle yemeğinin ardından ikinci b&ouml;l&uuml;m başlayacak. Her botta bir grup insan ve profesyonel bir rehber olacak. Turdan sonra turdaki fotoğrafları ve videoları satın alabilirsiniz.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<font face=\"raleway, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Sigorta</span></font></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Ekipman</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">t&uuml;m ulaşımlar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">a&ccedil;ık b&uuml;fe &ouml;ğle yemeği</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<font face=\"raleway, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">İ&ccedil;ecek</span></font></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">kişisel masraflar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">bahşişler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Otelden servis.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Yanınızda Getirin: Deniz Kıyafeti, G&uuml;neş Kremi, Havlu, Kamera</span></span></p>\n', '9-10 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '', 'Рафтинг', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Рафтинг по реке Даламан - одна из самых популярных программ дневных поездок в регионе Фетхие.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Время отправления: Калис 8:15 вечера Фетхие 08:00 Мёртвое море 07:10</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Время прибытия: приблизительно&nbsp; 18:30</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Скорость течения реки около 3-4. Рафтинг - это приключенческий и активный вид спорта, который проходит на свежем воздухе. На реке Даламан мы превратим этот вид спорта в удовольствие с помощью наших опытных и квалифицированных гидов и сотрудников. Гид на лодке поможет вам. Тем не менее, мы гарантируем, что вы промокнете, но получите массу удовольствия.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Тур будет состоять из двух частей. После тренировки и инструктажа мы займёмся первой частью рафтинга. Вторая часть начнется после обеда. На каждой лодке будет группа людей и профессиональный гид. Вы можете приобрести фотографии и видео вашего тура.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Страховка</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Оборудование</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Весь транспорт</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; &laquo;Шведский стол&raquo;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Напитки</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сервис из отеля.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Возьмите с собой: одежду для плаванья, солнцезащитный крем, полотенце, фотоаппарат.</span></span></p>\n', '9-10 часов', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
