(126, 'Chillout Day At Kayakoy Fethiye', 'Chillout-Day-At-Kayakoy-Fethiye', '399ca-chillout-day-at-kayafoy-1.jpg', 'dc9dc-kayakoy-01.jpg', '6185', 37, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">If you like to explore the area by your self and tired of city life, for some nature and peaceful area, you can join this tour.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick Up: Calis 09:30 Fethiye 09:45 Oludeniz 10:00 Hisaronu 10:45</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Drop Off: Approximately 18:00</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">We will take you to a fantastic place where nature meets history, Kayakoy Ghost Village. Walk around, discover the area, visit the Ghost Town or just sit and relax with the beautfiul scenery of the valley.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Kayakoy, Ghost Town was a Greek and Turkish mixed town. During the population exchange between Greece and Turkey, all the Greek people were moved to Greece and the city stayed abandoned and untouched so far. After a walk around you can visit the pottery and relax by the pool side, have some delicious pancakes and chill out. Lunch, snacks, drinks are not included to the price, transfer, map and area information is included.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Age Limit: 0+</span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">INCLUDED</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Transport</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<font face=\"raleway, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Map</span></font></li>\n	<li>\n		<font face=\"raleway, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Guide</span></font></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">EXCULED:</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Drinks</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Pick Up: Calis 09:30 Fethiye 09:45 Oludeniz 10:00 Hisaronu 10:45</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bring Along: Sun cream, Camera, Shoes, Hat</span></span></p>\n', '9-10 Hours', 0, '', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">English speaking tour guide.</span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">24 Hours before the tour.</span></p>\n', 1, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">If you like to explore the area by your self and tired of city life, for some nature and peaceful area, you can join this tour.&nbsp;</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 0, 89, 'Fethiye Karaköy Gezisi', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Şehir hayatından sıkıldıysanız, doğa ve huzur dolu bir yer arıyorsanız ve b&ouml;lgeyi keşfetmek istiyorsanız bize katılın. Doğanın tarihle buluştuğu Kayak&ouml;y&rsquo;e (Ghost Town) gidiyoruz. B&ouml;lgeyi dilediğiniz gibi keşfedin, y&uuml;r&uuml;y&uuml;şe &ccedil;ıkın ve vadinin muhteşem manzarasında kaybolun.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Alış Saati: &Ccedil;alış 09:30 Fethiye 09:45 &Ouml;l&uuml;deniz 10:00 Hisar&ouml;n&uuml; 10:45</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bırakış Saati: Tahmini 18:00</span></span></p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Kayak&ouml;y, bir T&uuml;rk-Yunan karma kasabasıdır. Yunanistan ile T&uuml;rkiye arasındaki n&uuml;fus takası anlasmasında buradaki t&uuml;m Yunan halkı Yunanistan&rsquo;a taşınmış ve şehir bug&uuml;ne kadar terkedilmiş olarak kalmıştır. Rahatlatan bir y&uuml;r&uuml;y&uuml;ş&uuml;n ardından alışveriş, yemek ve havuz başında keyif i&ccedil;in de vaktimiz olacak. Transfer, harita ve b&ouml;lge rehberliği fiyata dahil, &ouml;ğle yemeği, atıştırmalıklar ve i&ccedil;ecekler dahil değildir.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Profesyonel rehber</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">t&uuml;m ulaşımlar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<font face=\"raleway, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&Ouml;ğle yemeği</span></font></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">İ&ccedil;ecekler</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">kişisel masraflar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">bahşişler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Otelden servis.</span></p>\n', '', '9-10 Saat', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşan rehber.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '', 'Фетхие Каракей Путешествие', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Если вы устали от городской жизни, ищете место, наполненное природой и спокойствием, и хотите исследовать регион, присоединяйтесь к нам. Мы едем в Каякёй, это место, где природа встречается с историей. Исследуйте местность по своему желанию, отправляйтесь на прогулку и потеряйтесь в великолепных пейзажах долины.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Время отправления: 09:30 Фетхие 09:45 Мёртвое море 10:00 Хисарону 10:45</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Время прибытия: расчетное 18:00</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Каякёй - это смешанный турецко-греческий город. Этот город до настоящего времени остался заброшенным из-за обмена населением между Грецией и Турцией, по условиям договора все греки переехали в Грецию. После расслабляющей прогулки у нас будет время насладиться покупками, обедом, вы сможете расслабиться возле бассейна. Трансфер, карта и руководство области не включены в цену, обед, закуски и напитки также не включены.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Профессиональный гид</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Весь транспорт</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Обед</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Напитки&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сервис из отеля.</span></span></p>\n', '', '9-10 часов', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Русско-язычный или англоязычный гид.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(127, 'Fethiye Turkish Bath ', 'Fethiye-Turkish-Bath-', '05aa8-turkish-bath-01.jpg', '2be0f-turkish-bath-03.jpg', '6190', 37, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Hamam is a famous tradition of Ottoman and Turkey for centuries. Its known as Turkish Bath all over the world.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick Up: We will email you for the pick up time</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Drop Off: ...</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Hamam starts with a relaxation in a warm room. Here you will relax get get ready for a real bath. Than bather will move to main section where there is a marble area thay you lay on it. Be careful its hot. Here you will sweat and be ready for a full body wash.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">You can ask for a massage and soap massage. After the massage you will move to hot water taps and get cleaned. Final should be with a cold water wash and cooling room later. Optionally you may have peeling masks, oil massage, face and body masks and more for beauty. Our price includes the entrance and the regular bath. Soap wash, massage and masks are extra. We must leave a note that its best to start your holiday with a Hamam, so the sun tan you will have will last longer.</span></span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.35pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">INCLUDED</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Transport</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<font face=\"raleway, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Entrance Fee</span></font></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">EXCULED:</span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Exfoliation, Massage, Foam, Masks</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick Up: We will email you for the pick up time</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bring Along: Swimsuit</span></span></p>\n', '2-3 Hours', 0, '1', '', 0, 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">No guide needed.</span></span></p>\n', 0, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">24 Hours before the activity</span></span></p>\n', 0, '', 'surekli', 0, '', 1, '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Hamam is a famous tradition of Ottoman and Turkey for centuries. Its known as Turkish Bath all over the world.</span></p>\n', 1, 1, '18+', '6-17', '0-5', 0, 90, 'Hamam', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Hamam, Osmanlı İmparatorluğu ve T&uuml;rkiye&rsquo;nin &ccedil;ok eski bir geleneğidir. T&uuml;m d&uuml;nyada T&uuml;rk Hamamı olarak bilinir. Hamam sıcak bir odada rahatlama ile başlar. Burada dinlendikten sonra yıkanacağınız hamam b&ouml;l&uuml;m&uuml;ne ge&ccedil;ersiniz. G&ouml;bek taşında terleyip yıkanmaya hazır hale gelirsiniz.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Alış Saati: Detaylar i&ccedil;in sizinle iletişime ge&ccedil;ilecektir</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Bırakış Saati: ...</span></span></p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Tellaklardan masaj ve sabun banyosu talep edebilirsiniz. Masajın ardından muslukların başına ge&ccedil;ip tamamen yıkanırsınız. Finalde soğuk su ile yıkanılmalı ve soğuk odada dinlenilmelidir. İsteğe bağlı olarak y&uuml;z ve v&uuml;cut maskeleri ve yağlı masaj yaptırabilirsiniz. &Uuml;crete giriş ve standart yıkanma dahildir. Masajlar ve maskeler ekstradır. Tatile hamam ile başlamak en iyisidir. B&ouml;ylece bronzlaşmanın keyfi daha uzun s&uuml;rer.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura ne dahildir?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">giriş &uuml;creti</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">ulaşım</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<u><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">Bu tura dahil olmayanlar</span></span></strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Masaj, Kese, K&ouml;p&uuml;k Masajı, Maske</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">kişisel masraflar</span></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif;\">bahşişler</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Otelden servis.</span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Yanınızda Getirin: Deniz Kıyafeti</span></span></p>\n', '2 Saat', '<p>\n	-</p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Turdan 24 saat &ouml;nce.</span></p>\n', '', 'Хаммам', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Хаммам очень старая традиция Османской империи и Турции. Хаммам известен как турецкая баня во всем мире. Хаммам начинается с отдыха в теплой комнате. Отдохнув здесь, вы переходите в ванную комнату, где будете мыться. Пропотев вы ляжете на главный камень (дословно &laquo;камень для живота&raquo;) и будьте готовы к тому, что вас будут мыть.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Время отправления: с вами свяжутся для уточнения деталей</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Время прибытия: ...</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Вы можете заказать массаж и мыльную ванну. После массажа подойдите к&nbsp; крану и помойтесь полностью. После этого следует ополоснуться холодной водой и остаться в прохладной комнате. По желанию вы можете сделать маски для лица и тела и масляный массаж. Вход и стандартное купание включено в стоимость. Массажи и маски являются дополнительными. Лучше всего начинать с хаммама в начале отдыха. Таким образом загар будет держаться дольше.</span></span></p>\n', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что входит в этот тур?</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Вход</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Транспорт</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Что не входит в этот тур</u></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Массаж, нежный пилинг банной варежкой (Kese), Пенный массаж, маска</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Личные расходы</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">&bull; Чаевые</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Сервис из отеля</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Возьмите с собой: одежду для плаванья</span></span></p>\n', '2-3 часа', '', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">За 24 часа до тура.</span></span></p>\n', '',