(128, 'Speed Boat Hire ', 'Speed-Boat-Hire-', '80152-speed-boat-hire-3.jpg', '7bb29-speed-boat-hire-3.jpg', '6195', 37, '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">You can be your own captain and discover the area by yourself. Hire one of out speed boats with or without captain and have a great day on the sea. There are many secret beaches, amazing spots, coves, and more to discover at Oludeniz sea.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Pick Up: We will email you for the transfer time</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Drop Off: ...</span></span></p>\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 4.95pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">Speed boats are fully equipped and maintained. Comes with sun canopy and cold boxes for your drinks. There is a map for the best spots of the area and a mobile phone on board and petrol tank comes full which is enough to travel around during your rental period. There is also a spare petrol tank on boat. There are 2 time slots available every day. You can choose 09:00 to 13:00 morning period or 14:00 to 18:00 noon period. You can also hire the boat for full day.</span></span>