(139, 'Cappadocia Mix Tour', 'Cappadocia-Mix-Tour', '37654-open-air-museum.jpg', '09a3a-348f6-red-tour-museum.jpg', '1250', 23, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">İf you have one full day this tour is the best choice for you to book!!</span><br bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, \" vera=\"\" />\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">There are only places not to be missed on this tour.&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">&bull; Departure at 9.30 from the hotel (transfer included)</span><br bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, \" vera=\"\" />\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">&bull; Panorama of Goreme old town</span><br bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, \" vera=\"\" />\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">&bull; Panorama of Uchisar castle</span><br bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, \" vera=\"\" />\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">&bull; Pigeon Valley</span><br bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, \" vera=\"\" />\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">&bull; Zelve open-air museum. (ticket included)</span><br bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, \" vera=\"\" />\n	<span style=\"font-family: raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">&bull; Ozkonak underground city. (ticket included)</span><br bitstream=\"\" font