(140, 'Economic 2-Days Cappadocia Tour', 'Economic-2-Days-Cappadocia-Tour', '150cf-2-days-tur.jpg', 'b2a1a-2-days-tur-686x386.jpg', '1301', 23, '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">A more affordable 2-days magical Cappadocia tour. It starts by transferring you to the Airport from your hotel in Istanbul. This tour also includes a two-way ticket. Transfer from Cappadocia airport to your hotel. One night stay in a boutique hotel in Cappadocia. The next day a tour of the most beautiful places in Cappadocia.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">This tour can be tailored to your wishes.</span></span></p>\n', '<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">1-Day: Your pick up time will be notified after the time of booking. Transfer from your hotel in Istanbul to the airport to fly to Cappadocia, on arrival at the Cappadocia airport driver will be waiting for you at the exit door of the airport. He will take you to your Hotel. Rest of the day is yours.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">You can also participate in an activity of your choice.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">*Dervish show</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">*Turkish night</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">*You can also reserve a hot air balloon for the next day.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">If you want to make a reservation, you can inform us by mail.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:raleway,sans-serif;\">2-Day: You will be picked up f