(9, '17', '1400', 31, 'Harika..!', 'Bu muhteşem &ouml;tesi deneyimi bize yaşattığınız i&ccedil;in teşekk&uuml;r ederiz', '2019-09-10', 1),
(10, '139', '1250', 46, 'Great tour, amazing tour guide!!', 'İt was a great tour to spend a day in Cappadocia with my family. Small group of people and tour guide can speak really good english.  And also I wanted to say thanks to Blue eye tour while booking this tour I asked many questions and they answered with a passion they are always there to help about anything.', '2019-10-20', 1),
(11, '17', '1400', 45, 'Amazing life experiance!!', 'We did not book in advance so we had some hard time to find vacancy finally found on blue eye tour thank you blue eye for giving us such an amazing life experiance.', '2019-10-20', 1),
(14, '59', '1020', 45, 'Authentic Sufi ceremony.', 'The spiritual and symbolic Dervish ceremony is great worth to go when you are visiting Cappadocia. I thoroughly enjoyed the show and now want to learn more about the history and life of Mevlana.', '2019-10-20', 1),
(16, '58', '1010', 65, 'Great experience!', 'I think that an activity must be seen in turkey. reflecting the culture of Turkey, it was a fun. Dinner was very tasty and they offer unlimited alcohol service. In the meantime, Blue Eye offers transfer service from the hotel.', '2020-01-08', 1),
(17, '17', '1400', 65, 'It was exciting', 'I\'ve been dreaming of flying balloons for a year. I finally made it. It was very exciting for me. I had also booked a Turkish night show from blue eye. I made a separate comment for turkish night also. I thank the Blue Eye Tour for their help.', '2020-01-08', 1),
(18, '139', '1250', 11, 'Amazing experience', 'Our tour was lovely. The van picked us on time and dropped us back to our hotel. The tour guide, Asim was very good. He took the time and not only explained the rich history behind all the places we visited in the tour but also took all of our pictures without any complaint. We visited a lot of beautiful places in Kappadocia, including the underground city, the open air museum and many more. Lunch was included as well in the tour and it was very yummy. Would definitely recommend taking this tour and Definitely with Asim as your tour guide!!', '2020-01-09', 1),
(19, '139', '1250', 66, 'Great Tour to Spend a Day', 'I had just one day in Cappadocia and there are two tours red and green but I don&rsquo;t have two days to join them each day so I needed a tour shows me red and green tours best places in one day. By searching online I found blue eye tour making a mix tour. I had a great time with this tour company they are really friendly and professional tour guide explains everything in detail.\r\nTHANK YOU BLUE EYE ALL THE BEST!!!!', '2020-01-09', 1),
(23, '59', '1020', 68, 'Amazing experience', 'Thank you for organizing Sema Whirling Dervish Ceremony! It was an amazing night!Omar was great on communication and punctuality. His driver even drove us complementary to the city center ot Urgup! Highly recommended travel company!', '2020-01-09', 1),
(24, '8', '1200', 67, 'Red &amp; Green Tour', 'The Blue Eye Travel is a great agency, they helped me and advice me the appropriate time especially when i am taking an evening flight. Their advice is really insightful that gave us the assurance that we enjoy and they make sure we wont miss the tour and of course our flight :-P. However, some of us on the green tour couldn\'t really understand all the explanation due to the accent. But on the red tour, the guide is really loud and clear!! kudos to him!\r\n\r\nIn addition, their arrangement of the airport transfer was seamless. And i do recommend them as they are very trustworthy and the group are small which gave us more personal communication and better insights. Great Job to Omar and team!! Cheers', '2020-01-09', 1),
(25, '59', '1020', 69, 'Sema Ceremony - A must do in Turkey', 'It is soul touching performance of the Sufi dancers, the music was enchanting and the whirling was mesmering. I guess my expectation was too much, that I felt there was a miss, which I am not able to pinpoint.', '2020-01-09', 1),
(26, '33', '1910', 70, 'Very exciting activity.', 'Our tour leader made very crazy moves. Even watching were very excited. Our only regret was not to take two hours, one hour was too short for this activity.\r\nOne advice for those who want to take this tour is to take a 2-hour sunset tour.', '2020-01-10', 1),
(27, '34', '1920', 71, 'Excited and worthy', 'We have toured many valleys, it is easy to drive, the tour leader gives brief information about the valleys and even helped us take photos. This tour is very meaningful to do at sunset. \r\nBefore back to the hotel, we watched the sunset from the rose valley.', '2020-01-10', 1),
(29, '31', '1800', 73, 'Amazing sunset!', 'As someone who loves horses, I had so much fun on this tour. We climbed from the inside of the valleys to the highest hills and watched the sunset. The tour leader was very concerned.', '2020-01-10', 1),
(31, '58', '1010', 75, 'Great fun !!', 'Pick-up from the hotel was on time. Concerned staff and delicious food. The dance team was very good at work and made us laugh. The belly dancer gathered a couple of guys and told them to dance like her, which was funny. Alcohol free.                                                         \r\n                                 Thanks to Blue Eye for arranging this beautiful night for us.', '2020-01-10', 1),
(32, '34', '1920', 72, 'Enjoyable!', 'They pick it up from the hotel and drop it back to the hotel. They give me a helmet and a mask. It can be a little dusty. There were too many people at the sunset point but should be the best place to watch the sunset. We really enjoyed this tour. By the way, It is possible to join this tour after the daily tour.', '2020-01-10', 1),
(33, '15', '1300', 74, 'Good price with good service', 'This place full of history, just like Goreme open-air museum. Nature is also so beautiful love valley, pasha bagı valley, uchisar castle. We also enjoyed pottery workshops they let me to make simple pottery. Lunch was delicious. The tour guide\'s relevance were very good from the morning meeting to the end of the tour. The tour is not too long so we are not too tired.', '2020-01-18', 1),
(34, '8', '1200', 91, 'Excelente experiencia', 'Hicimos dos tours con esta agencia, el green tour y el de los globos aerost&aacute;ticos. Ambos muy buenos, pasaron a buscarnos al hotel incluyeron las comidas y movilizacion.\r\nCotizando varios fue uno de los m&aacute;s convenientes econ&oacute;micamente.', '2020-01-25', 1),
(35, '17', '1400', 90, 'Maravilloso', 'Una experiencia realmente hermosa de la cual no te puedes perder si es que est&aacute;s en cappadocia, nosotras lo hicimos al amantes y lo recomendamos al 100%', '2020-01-25', 1),
(36, '17', '1400', 92, 'Hermosa experiencia.', 'Muy buen servicio y super bien organizado, una experiencia unica!', '2020-01-25', 1),
(37, '8', '1200', 92, 'Muy bueno.', 'Este tour es muy bonito ya que te muestran un paisaje unico y aprendes muchas cosas!', '2020-01-25', 1),
(38, '8', '1200', 90, 'Excelente', 'Nos pasaron a buscar al hotel temprano y conocimos lugares por por nuestra cuenta no hubi&eacute;ramos conocido, realmente genial.', '2020-01-25', 1),
(39, '17', '1400', 91, 'So&ntilde;ado', 'Es una experiencia hermosa que debes vivir si visitas Turqu&iacute;a. \r\nEl viaje en globo fue incre&iacute;ble, la hora de recogida fue muy puntual y pudimos ver a la perfecci&oacute;n el amanecer arriba del globo, al bajar no dieron una copa de champa&ntilde;a y en la ma&ntilde;ana antes de subir desayuno. La verdad me voy feliz con mi experiencia.', '2020-01-25', 1),
(41, '17', '1400', 10, 'Herkese &ouml;neriririm', '&Ccedil;ok g&uuml;zel zaman ge&ccedil;irdik, herkese &ouml;neririm)', '2020-03-04', 1),
(43, '17', '1400', 144, 'Must do in Cappadocia!', 'Everything was perfect. \r\nBecause of the pandemic, there was no breakfast before the flight and celebration after flight, but the price was very affordable and it was very comfortable with very few people in the basket. \r\nThank you so much.', '2020-10-29', 1),
(44, '34', '1920', 146, 'Excited and recommend ..', 'At the beginning I thought it was dangerous, but it wasn\'t like that at all. I used ATV very comfortably.\r\nLove valley is very beautiful. unique sunset tour.', '2020-10-29', 1),
(45, '3', '1500', 147, 'Fantastic view from the sky!!', 'Thank you Blue Eye Tour for the amazing experience that we had. Such a professional team from start to the end. The flight was amazing with beautiful views over valleys.  \r\n\r\nSpecially, Thanks to our pilot. He is very professional, experienced.', '2020-10-31', 1),
(46, '3', '1500', 148, 'Everyone should try', 'We have chosen the comfort flight. It was a much more comfortable flight experience with fewer people. Thanks to our pilot for such an amazing experience', '2020-10-31', 1),
(47, '59', '1020', 149, 'Very interesting activity and affordable price!', 'I saw that this activity was organized by Blue Eye Tour on the Tripadvisor, but I booked it on this website because it was more affordable and I was very pleased.\r\nI was dizzy as they whirled around and still don\'t know how they do it. Interesting.', '2020-10-31', 1),
(48, '17', '1400', 150, 'Not to be missed experience', 'This is a not to be missed experience while in Cappadocia and we are very pleased we chose blue eye tour. Booking was super easy, we just walked into their office in G&ouml;reme the day before.\r\nOn time pick-up from our Hotel.\r\nPilot was very nice! Felt very safe. \r\nWould definitely use blue eye tour for booking again, highly recommend! Thanks for an awesome start to the day!', '2020-10-31', 1),
(49, '17', '1400', 152, 'Make a wish in the air!', 'Responsible and responsive customer service by Blue Eye. Good service provided by the hot air ballon company. Smooth ride with beautiful scenery. Personally speaking, my favorite part of the tour was seeing the staff inflating the ballon and preparing everything before take off. That was the most fun to witness. Unique experience.', '2021-01-07', 1);
